a49a07cf75a202abe74d9d3afd2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=79932a4adac9da4404681d369dec4258"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide for mastering the CCNP Enterprise Design ENSLD 300-420 exam. Covering key topics such as advanced addressing, routing solutions, enterprise campus networks, WAN, and network automation, this guide provides detailed study plans, quizzes, and chapter-end exercises. Expert authors Anthony Bruno and Steve Jordan offer tips to improve conceptual knowledge and hands-on skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="31daysbeforeyourciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-1"&gt;&lt;a id="31daysbeforeyourciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/31daysbeforeyourciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-1_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=f7f6389aef14353c8896a7509adfb60865cb6ab54d1038cd96cd498db518beb1"&gt;31 Days Before your Cisco Certified Support Technician (CCST) Networking 100-150 Exam&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0e5b6246056ce59786b9b2ad731870c4035a9459.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f5e6c2f36001ca53cf692b92384b81e3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This practical, handy guide provides a 31-day study plan for the CCST Networking 100-150 exam. It covers key topics like standards, addressing, infrastructure, and security in short, easy-to-review summaries. You'll start each day with a detailed plan and study resources for deeper exploration. With expert advice, checklists, and exam preparation strategies, this guide helps you stay organized and ready for exam success, all while fitting study time into your busy schedule.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccnpandcciecollaborationcoreclcor350-801officialcertguide2ande"&gt;&lt;a id="ccnpandcciecollaborationcoreclcor350-801officialcertguide2ande" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ccnpandcciecollaborationcoreclcor350-801officialcertguide2ande_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=db37dcd51eff7cbb90a2f63ab1cdd01b08e96191aa9893c6ef49a60c12e2116e"&gt;CCNP and CCIE Collaboration Core CLCOR 350-801 Official Cert Guide, 2/e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c17a128b78aa63a03f34f853b6eb76cb94a8dbd5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5c07fce029a2627f7b20113f1e518e05"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide to help you prepare for the CCNP and CCIE CLCOR 350-801 exam. Covering topics like infrastructure, protocols, codecs, call control, QoS, and Webex, it offers detailed study plans, quizzes, and chapter-end exercises. Expert Jason Ball provides preparation tips to improve your knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccnpandcciedatacentercoredccor350-601officialcertguide2ande"&gt;&lt;a id="ccnpandcciedatacentercoredccor350-601officialcertguide2ande" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ccnpandcciedatacentercoredccor350-601officialcertguide2ande_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=ba071e0cf17aeb6b9ace4b00548fc9aa9f3f891edba4d5e99584072dde6ded2a"&gt;CCNP and CCIE Data Center Core DCCOR 350-601 Official Cert Guide, 2/e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9b86121866b830de816d590b797209fb9d952829.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0a759bd4eaabaabf2de81ca7a3269823"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide to help you prepare for the CCNP and CCIE Data Center Core DCCOR 350-601 exam. This guide covers key topics like networking, compute, storage networks, automation, and security. With detailed study plans, quizzes, and chapter-end exercises, it ensures you're fully prepared. Cisco experts Somit Maloo, Iskren Nikolov, and Firas Ahmed provide tips to help you strengthen both your conceptual knowledge and hands-on skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccnpandcciesecuritycorescor350-701examcram"&gt;&lt;a id="ccnpandcciesecuritycorescor350-701examcram" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ccnpandcciesecuritycorescor350-701examcram_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=f06f56fc2ef3c1352c25007033d556f479c443bac135488a07aded9afa5118b4"&gt;CCNP and CCIE Security Core SCOR 350 - 701 Exam Cram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/da087826f93587071aad70839304722bd3570ff6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0055fabade894a7a80d40a06e43ea3fb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed to help you pass the CCNP and CCIE Security Core SCOR 350-701 exam, this Exam Cram includes thorough coverage of every exam topic, quizzes, review questions, tips, and a helpful Cram Sheet for quick review. Key topics include security vulnerabilities, AAA configuration, segmentation, cloud security, traffic redirection, Cisco Umbrella, and multifactor authentication strategies.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccnpdatacenterapplicationcentricinfrastructure300-620dcaciofficial"&gt;&lt;a id="ccnpdatacenterapplicationcentricinfrastructure300-620dcaciofficial" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ccnpdatacenterapplicationcentricinfrastructure300-620dcaciofficial_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=35dbce37243fac42ebdf0eb602ff3d1afae75af1f6e94e3a32284193f5989d7b"&gt;CCNP Data Center Application Centric Infrastructure 300-620 DCACI Official Cert Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ec9631e5aebc832ab482c6b53e550dac2398a20d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5bdd827a89623d138836f8378462225d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide to help you prepare for the CCNP Data Center Application Centric Infrastructure DCACI 300-620 exam. It covers key topics like ACI fabric infrastructure, packet forwarding, external network connectivity, integrations, and ACI management. With chapter-opening quizzes, exam prep tasks, and exercises, this guide provides a structured study routine. Cisco expert Ammar Ahmadi offers preparation tips to enhance your knowledge and hands-on skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccnpsecurityciscosecurefirewallandintrusionpreventionsystemofficia"&gt;&lt;a id="ccnpsecurityciscosecurefirewallandintrusionpreventionsystemofficia" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ccnpsecurityciscosecurefirewallandintrusionpreventionsystemofficia_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=fd2bb2ed07b40151415d369dd8f4e110498edce7b65eca25afcaf7bea59dbacf"&gt;CCNP Security Cisco Secure Firewall and Intrusion Prevention System Official Cert Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/73dc862e756a49df7b0c9429441185134b285e76.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=22a50146e81e6cf539ad422b06459df8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide to help you study for the CCNP Security exam on Cisco Secure Firewall and IPS (formerly Cisco Firepower). It offers detailed study plans, quizzes, and chapter-end exercises to master key topics like configurations, integrations, deployments, and troubleshooting. Cisco security expert Nazmul Rajib provide preparation tips and tricks to ensure you're fully prepared for exam success.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-150officialcertgu"&gt;&lt;a id="ciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-150officialcertgu" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianccstnetworking100-150officialcertgu_preview.pdf?t=st=1759594648~exp=1759681048~hmac=ca74053761f6f9d8d4ae5b13bce07acd49b46aa8af87e34f2e2b9518d5cde8e4"&gt;Cisco Certified Support Technician CCST 100-150 Networking Official Cert Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9cf7bfa8140029a633d1025405f9fdc031cf6abb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e361ae71563a1abf9a973729c47f4c0c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Official Cert Guide to help you prepare for the CCST Networking 100-150 exam. Covering topics like standards, addressing, infrastructure, diagnostics, and security, it offers detailed study plans, quizzes, and chapter-end exercises. Expert Russ White provides preparation tips to improve your knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
