      <title>World of Darkness: Month of Darkness 2025 Physical Book Bundle by Renegade Game Studios</title>
      <author>Renegade Game Studios</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//books/world-darkness-month-darkness-2025-physical-book-bundle-renegade-game-studios-books</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">e772ef9eb6693444ea5bc2cca82a5b7755ee7e8c</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Oct 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/adba645bb7c4bed2500a6ab9514c37c0dcba9aa2.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=26312c8e49463f745c5db56920c981e8"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/61f819040702cf2c9795844bd0484faddf05797e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=29814a77a56d2e075dbf6be7cd66b742"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Embrace the World of Darkness, Physically&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create an original vampire character, torn between survival, supremacy, and your unquenchable thirst for mortal blood with the Month of Darkness 2025 Physical Bundle by Renegade Game Studios! This collection of Fifth Edition tomes marks a triumphant return to Vampire: The Masquerade’s original vision—boldly modernized for the 21st century with streamlined gameplay and quality-of-life updates. The rules have been reimagined, yet the deep lore remains, advancing the metaplot and revealing the latest twists in the World of Darkness. Host the bloodiest, most unforgettable TTRPG nights—and help support the charity of your choice with your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $55 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_secondinquisition_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Second Inquisition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_falloflondonchronicle_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Fall of London Chronicle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_sabbattheblackhandsourcebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Sabbat The Black Hand Sourcebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt150"&gt;Pay $150 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_playersguide_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Player's Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#werewolftheapocalypserpg_5theditioncorerulebook_physical"&gt;Werewolf The Apocalypse RPG: 5th Edition Core Rulebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_blood-stainedlovesourcebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Blood-Stained Love Sourcebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vampirethemasquerade_rpg_thecrimsongutterchroniclebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - The Crimson Gutter Chronicle Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#hunterthereckoningrpg_linesdrawninbloodchroniclebook_physical"&gt;Hunter The Reckoning RPG: Lines Drawn in Blood Chronicle Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $55 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_secondinquisition_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_secondinquisition_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Second Inquisition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2d05c9a1617c5d94a16a62b6f6595b8eb77f7193.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=852896388548bda9bbfe098c25938fac"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Crimson Gutter provides a starter chronicle, designed to help novice or experienced Storytellers run any introductory game of Vampire: The Masquerade. The Crimson Gutter chronicle introduces core concepts during play such as feeding, the sects (Anarchs, Camarilla), and the Masquerade itself while giving the players' characters a chance to carve a niche for themselves among the Kindred.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_falloflondonchronicle_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_falloflondonchronicle_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Fall of London Chronicle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/04459f5474a80a258b310671f33597e800f4b4eb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8b832499b4a418f38b4634becb1dac24"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Fall of London is a Chronicle set in London in 2012, exploring the events that led to the canonical destruction of the city’s Kindred by the Second Inquisition. It is centered around a group of members of the Cult of Mithras who are awakened during the turmoil to retrieve five ancient relics of the Kindred god-ruler of Britain.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_sabbattheblackhandsourcebook_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_sabbattheblackhandsourcebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Sabbat The Black Hand Sourcebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5983a298be1baf26b4512e54fb3d92d04bf72baf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0dd209e76c81281a887e35bfeeead346"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sabbat: The Black Hand is a supplement for the Vampire: The Masquerade Roleplaying Game, outlining in detail the lore and background of the Sabbat, including new Paths and Disciplines, histories, and new Storyteller resources for a richer roleplaying experience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt150"&gt;Pay $150 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_playersguide_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_playersguide_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Player's Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/179f7657ac48294fb51691964cd020c70656e951.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=04e2373d4e08b7f1592dc35b76a3d935"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This book collects new character-building options, powers, guides for playing together and alone and virtually, and new ways to use the old rules of Vampire: The Masquerade. The Players Guide is the perfect companion to the core Vampire: The Masquerade rulebook!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="werewolftheapocalypserpg_5theditioncorerulebook_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="werewolftheapocalypserpg_5theditioncorerulebook_physical"&gt;Werewolf The Apocalypse RPG: 5th Edition Core Rulebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0aff651c673efb3c402624eaffc074c1c1aa3cec.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1af6199e73e144d702b5f1a8ae3430fa"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a new generation Garou, you will confront the forces of destruction, avarice, and greed ravaging the earth-mother. Utilize the 5th edition Storyteller system to create your chronicles within the World of Darkness. Includes everything you need to know to build your own character or guide a troupe as they explore their new forms. As a werewolf, build your legend, vie for renown, and fight to take back what has been lost. Join one of eleven tribes, each unique and rich with narrative depth for players to explore, and Storytellers to utilize. This 300+ page PDF also includes an introductory story to guide new Werewolf players and veteran World of Darkness enthusiasts through their first game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_blood-stainedlovesourcebook_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_blood-stainedlovesourcebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - Blood-Stained Love Sourcebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e0dab44f3e2df1c9e4b1ca4fea11180de44212c1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4ba5840088fd62f27ef884a414ee1dda"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your game of personal and political horror to include wide-eyed lovers and manipulative monsters. The book is for Storytellers and players alike, giving you tools, techniques and advice on how to bring romance to the undead. This book includes 6 six fleshed out storytelling characters and six detailed story concepts, all designed to maximize romance potential.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_thecrimsongutterchroniclebook_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="vampirethemasquerade_rpg_thecrimsongutterchroniclebook_physical"&gt;Vampire The Masquerade: RPG - The Crimson Gutter Chronicle Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e0185ef24e9e13f797e9ee217c8ab3f5c8b2d9ed.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=57758f8f9bd83ca7763ea28f56fbcb76"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Crimson Gutter provides a starter chronicle, designed to help novice or experienced Storytellers run any introductory game of Vampire: The Masquerade. The Crimson Gutter chronicle introduces core concepts during play such as feeding, the sects (Anarchs, Camarilla), and the Masquerade itself while giving the players' characters a chance to carve a niche for themselves among the Kindred.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hunterthereckoningrpg_linesdrawninbloodchroniclebook_physical"&gt;&lt;a id="hunterthereckoningrpg_linesdrawninbloodchroniclebook_physical"&gt;Hunter The Reckoning RPG: Lines Drawn in Blood Chronicle Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2be1c16fa15c2677f72c8fad52248880515167b3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=35a0f045e96355d1d93410e0c58386c3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;What lines are you willing to cross when you push back against the evil that walks among us? Lines Drawn in Blood presents a series of four stories that can be played individually or linked together to tell an entire chronicle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
      <category>books</category>
      <category>Humble RPG Bundle</category>
      <category>8 books</category>
      <category>$380 Value</category>
    </item>
