terial Instances: 229&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 297&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedcastleenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedcastleenvironment"&gt;Stylized Castle Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/811509f78c06ec0818faf79bb7191744904eacb1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a2d9abd166cd980056da6582ea42e58a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Stylized Castle Environment with 65 Assets. Many different types of Assets help you create or polish your Environments. All Assets are made with unique concepts, and a Showcased Example level is also included in the Project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gameready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 65&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 70&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 87&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 4K, 2K, 1K:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="windmill"&gt;&lt;a id="windmill"&gt;Windmill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4d253e85e933362b97fff57352724a87d201699f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=600f2dca800466e698dc7425adafd713"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This environment pack features 5 uniquely crafted meshes, including all showcased assets in high quality. Built with performance in mind, it's fully optimized for game-ready projects and virtual production.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 5 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="driveableandanimatedretrocyberpunkhovercar02unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="driveableandanimatedretrocyberpunkhovercar02unrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/HA4EMd6_DZ0"&gt;Driveable / Animated Retro Cyberpunk Hover Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Driveable / Animated Retro Cyberpunk Hover Car with customizable materials, you can adjust color/dirt in Material Instance parameters, drive the car in your game level, and fly with the car through your scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: (Please include a full, comprehensive list of the features of the product)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With Custom Cyberpunk Interior&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Driveable / Animated&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blueprint Prefab&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 9&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 9&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints : 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 44&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="materialassignmenttool"&gt;&lt;a id="materialassignmenttool" href="https://youtu.be/gZCcOSubK-g"&gt;Material Assignment Tool&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of being a leading art outsourcing company.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Material Assignment tool makes tracking static mesh assets with standard slots easy and allows you to bulk assign materials to them all at once.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As an art outsourcing company, our primary focus has been delivering exceptional visual assets, animations, and art production services to game developers. However, recognizing the industry's evolving needs and the importance of efficient workflows, we have embarked on the development of our groundbreaking code plugin tool.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple material assignments for equivalent static mesh actors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Code Modules MaterialAssignment(Editor)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;MaterialAssignmentManger(Editor)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes 6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Network Replicated No&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hatchbackcardriveableandanimatedandrealistic"&gt;&lt;a id="hatchbackcardriveableandanimatedandrealistic" href="https://youtu.be/sBNzaVWk-28"&gt;Hatchback Car Driveable / Animated / Realistic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;HatchBack Car is Driveable / Animated / Realistic / Customizable, AAA Quality, and Fully Customizable with separated Parts / Blueprints / Material İnstances, There are Dirt / Roughness / Metallic / Emissive / Color parameters in material instances so that you can arrange materials easily; the Vehicle will be in one blueprint and also six separated meshes so you will be able to use as you wish to, great prop for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between clean / dirty , old materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button animating car doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 13&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.19 , 4.20 , 4.21 , 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunk"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunk" href="https://youtu.be/K1bhBMdqWq0"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54d5293ed9ca7376c5cb1fd91cc39acea90b0c44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=75b889d5b7aeec7511da305f0e5a7546"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Themed Sound Effect Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="modularurbancityassetmegapack"&gt;&lt;a id="modularurbancityassetmegapack"&gt;Modular Urban City Asset Megapack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/082d7d326ccff1c07f5550eb4ac7f5d2636faf73.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=be25e8d4e72f5013bf816bdb22048257"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A fully modular urban city level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are two example levels included, one which has been quickly optimized to run 60+ FPS and another where you can show how the entire level was created using the modular pieces found throughout the pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Atmospheric Showcase Example.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Over 400 assets including store branding, modular pieces, and 160+ unique assets to populate the environments with everything from benches to bicycles to CCTV cameras.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;80 signs and posters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Premade distance buildings to populate your skylines with, as well as various merged streets from our example level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Various skyscrapers for your skylines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Three entirely unique environments in one scene! The scene includes modular sets for city streets, train platforms and the train ticket booth area!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Various Blueprints to help speed up the population of the environment from curb splines to platform notice boards with customizable text parameters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="victorianstreet"&gt;&lt;a id="victorianstreet" href="https://youtu.be/guYsC_C8LUU"&gt;Victorian Street&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Victorian Street&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring the atmosphere of 19th-century London into your projects with Victorian Street, a highly detailed environment pack crafted for cinematic and game-ready experiences. Designed with modular architecture, realistic cobblestone streets, and authentic period details, this pack delivers everything you need to recreate the charm of Victorian London.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Authentic Victorian-era buildings with red-brick and stone facades&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Detailed cobblestone roads, sidewalks, and vintage shopfronts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Period-accurate props: Union Jack flags, signage, lamps, and awnings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular design for flexible scene building&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for Unreal Engine (Nanite &amp;amp; Lumen supported)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Perfect for games, cinematics, VR, and historical visualizations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Step into the world of Victorian London and bring your story to life with Victorian Street.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="hyperscalableinteractionsystemv3"&gt;&lt;a id="hyperscalableinteractionsystemv3" href="https://youtu.be/l5ROlyRAsH4"&gt;Hyper Scalable Interaction System v3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyper Scalable Interaction System v3&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Add plug-and-play interaction to any actor with support for prompts, progress bars, conditions, and network replication.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Used in chests, doors, NPCs, items, switches, and more. Fully compatible with keyboard, mouse, or gamepad.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;No code required. Works in Adventure, RPG, Co-op, and Simulation games.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Also included within our flagship product MST Pro.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Key features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Interact with any object in the world.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implemented in an abstract way so you can use it easily on any system without any problem.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Dynamic interact icons (E key)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Shows dynamic interact text (Hold E to X)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Shows interactable in radius so they can be found easily. Handy for when in a Forrest or in the dark.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Predefined interaction types like Interact, Toggle, Grab&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Works easily via interfaces&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Advanced logic options: e.g. Turn these off and these on when button is down. Optional reverse.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Many advanced examples&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Clickable buttons&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Toggle buttons&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Intractable Pull Chain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Intractable Crank&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Intractable Switch/Lever&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Doors and fireplaces&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Intractable Lights&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Compatibility:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions -&amp;nbsp;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="romanvolcanictemple"&gt;&lt;a id="romanvolcanictemple" href="https://youtu.be/8mF6MgYn0Cw"&gt;Roman Volcanic Temple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Roman Volcanic Temple Environment with 178 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 178 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 92&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 168&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1024, 2048, 4096&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Playable Area Size: 180m x 90m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Total Size: 500m x 500m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedmedievaltown"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedmedievaltown" href="https://youtu.be/3l_HlS8FWKw"&gt;Stylized Medieval Town&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Modular Stylized Medieval Town with 65 Assets. There is a lot of different type of Assets to help you create or polish your Environments. All Assets made with unique concepts and Showcased Example level is also included in Project. (Foliage is updated in the demo level for optimization.)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 65 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 82&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 114&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1024, 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.27, 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="morbidmotions_animationsandposes"&gt;&lt;a id="morbidmotions_animationsandposes" href="https://youtu.be/f7ValqvU2ms"&gt;Morbid Motions : Animations and Poses&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This animation pack includes a set of 57 animations 25 poses compatible with MannyUE5 skeleton.   &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;⚠️ Note:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Volumes 1 and 2 have been merged into a single asset pack: Morbid Motions: Animations and Poses.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Support: ursa.animation@gmail.com&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details - &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rigged to Epic skeleton: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scaled to Epic skeleton: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If rigged to the Epic skeleton, IK bones are included: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Animations: 57 animations +26 static poses&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animation types : in place&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="modularsci-fifactory"&gt;&lt;a id="modularsci-fifactory"&gt;Modular Sci-Fi Factory&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aec234f7abaf10863b789534e9945b1bbbcecfb8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=61f04bc892926f51a54814559580a604"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greetings !&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beneath flickering signs and humming ducts, the factory breathes with quiet power.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This sci-fi environment blends modular precision with industrial grit perfect for space corridors, research labs, and futuristic production facilities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Built for performance and detail, this environment is as efficient as it is atmospheric.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What’s Included: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular walls, ceilings, floors, and large corridor sections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Decals, signage sheets, and customizable material colors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lighting blueprints with adjustable emissive, blink, and intensity settings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Doors with lock states, UI panels, and level streaming support&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Flashlight system, note UIs, and tile-based texture workflow&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite-ready assets for optimized GPU performance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Prebuilt maps with streaming corridors and color variants&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got a question or need assistance? Feel free to contact us anytime at info@akairo.io we're here to help with technical support, suggestions, refunds, or any of your requests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mid-centurybrutalistdatacentre"&gt;&lt;a id="mid-centurybrutalistdatacentre"&gt;Mid-century Brutalist Data Centre&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c24e561cead7cf835f2ca083e015329893094684.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b2796fdf077e8241c069243ab28f05d9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A pack of over 100 props that all come together to create a beautiful environment filled with Mid-Century technology gently laid out in a brutalist office space.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Note: This project is lit entirely with Lumen! Emissive squares are the lighting source and the example scenes will not light unless lumen is enabled. Assets still function correctly with other lighting methods.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Includes:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Over 100 props&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Designed on a shared material system to take advantage of Nanite.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A hand crafted demonstration scene filled with all the assets.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Hand designed assets based on Mid-Century to late 80s technology.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully controllable material colour setup&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;This product supports (and is specifically built for) Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.1+&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 123&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 82&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 121&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 128-4096&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Windows&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Important/Additional Notes: The assets in this pack are designed around a shared material system, assets might look as if they have a lot of materials, this is on purpose as we were trying a different approach with this pack as it reduces the amount of textures required.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedlostruins"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedlostruins" href="https://youtu.be/z1cBhReFuKY"&gt;Stylized Lost Ruins&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5c049ff89fc3edc91ae0cbb535c4996a1f6c4224.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=de2d295a6332b8441b0fa738d5d11db8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Stylized Lost Ruins Environment with 101 Assets. There are many different types of Assets to help you create or polish your Environments.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Game-ready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 101&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 108&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 160&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K, 2K&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="africanvillage"&gt;&lt;a id="africanvillage"&gt;African Village&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/528b56a64ff848708a897c8499e188e960011bbc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2e6b8ea87c212c83e323139af3dc25e8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;African Village Environment with 164 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects. Bring the heart of the African savanna to life with this modular village pack. Designed for Unreal Engine, this asset set features handcrafted huts, native props, dry landscape elements, and a vivid atmosphere ideal for immersive storytelling.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes Showcased Preassembled Scene&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any kind of Virtual Production levels, here is the pack that you get and use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic savanna trees, rocks, and ground textures&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Traditional household props (stools, clay pots, woven baskets, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Village fencing, seating areas&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic dry grass and landscape elements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and clean UV mapping&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully optimized for real-time use&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="coastalwetlandandrailroadbridge"&gt;&lt;a id="coastalwetlandandrailroadbridge"&gt;Coastal Wetland &amp; Railroad Bridge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3a369a630a867cdac4f2b942d0968801e3d6a826.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7a526114b51ea3cf7e274491a63dae17"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*On the example levels, it's helpful to check ""Extend Default Luminance Range in Auto Exposure Settings"" to get the correct exposure values. Otherwise exposure ranges will not be correct*&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*This project runs with Distance Field Meshes + SSGI enabled. Dynamic lighting. Enable that for the best visual quality. *&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*If you are running into issues with loading the main level enable these plugins or download the project as an entire project, not just an asset pack*&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""HDRIBackdrop"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""Landmass"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""SunPosition"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""GPULightmass"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""Water"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;""Name"": ""ShallowWater"",&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our latest pack for you to dive into: This old railway snakes along a polluted coastal zone, where the river meets the sea. Includes an advanced spline system can be used to create any type of railroad, concrete box girder bridge, lift bridge, utility poles, gas pipelines, and more! Snap splines together and create intersections!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These assets are set up by default for First Person/VR games with a texel ratio of 10.24ppm for all your assets!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="industrialharbourenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="industrialharbourenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/o3RR6HLReL4"&gt;Industrial Harbour Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Industrial Harbour Environment with 106 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 106 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 125&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 210&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1024, 2048, 4096&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Playable Area Size: 208m x 82m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Total Size: 237m x 152m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedasiantemple"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedasiantemple"&gt;Stylized Asian Temple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dccbac8fc7bae5b3d5651d6e1947c06dfe19c584.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=38cf31e2cc541a1c1f30e1a43901a309"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stylized FPS Asian Temple (Modular) Stylized FPS Asian Temple (Modular) is a high-quality, modular asset pack including a wide variety of easy-to-assemble modular building assets and high-quality props. You can quickly iterate between mesh and material variations to populate and polish your game environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 142 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 130&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 264&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1024, 2048, 4096&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.27, 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Playable Area Size: 97m x 93m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Total Size: 107m x 93m&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="swimanimations"&gt;&lt;a id="swimanimations" href="https://youtu.be/t9nooM6nyaE"&gt;Swim | Animations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Swimming Animation Set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack includes InPlace , RootMotion, Transitions of high-quality hand key swimming animations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There is no water scene and no props included in this pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;UPDATES 1.3 - Sept 2024 -&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;a new swim back animation has been added InPlace/RootMotion&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Torpedo loop animation has been added&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;the new added animations have been retargeted to UE4 Mannequin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Video 1.3 - Updates Sept 2024&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;UPDATES 1.2 :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our animation library has been expanded&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We've added IK Retargeting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animations have been retargeted to the UE4 Mannequin character (there is a separate folder with his animations)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;UPDATES 1.1 :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Resolved IK bone issues for both Unreal Engine files and .fbx files&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animation library has been expanded with a few more animations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Included Animations:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim Idle (3 variations)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim Forward (6 variations, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim Forward lean Left/Right for all variations (no root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim Backward (2 variations, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim Left/Right (with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Jump in water Start (2 variations, each with Left and Right Leg, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Jump in water air loop (2 variations)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Jump in water End (3 variations, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dive under water (2 variations, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim to surface (with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Underwater locomotion (walk/run, with and without root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drowning, Dying, Dead&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Turn Left (root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Turn Right (root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;9 Dynamic Transitions ( 6 of them also have also root motion)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Working under water (hammering and cutting &amp;gt; Left and Right hand)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Torpedo 4 directions InPlace/RootMotion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swim backward C , 2 directions InPlace/RootMotion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="guitaristanimations"&gt;&lt;a id="guitaristanimations" href="https://youtu.be/YzNxci4UhKA"&gt;Guitarist | Animations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ This asset pack contains 59 animation assets, including variations ,transitions, designed for both UE5 and UE4 skeletons. Perfect for casual or performance scenes involving a Guitarist NPC.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Showcase Video&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tutorial Video&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;⚠️ Note:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Guitar meshes should be socketed to the spine_02 for UE5 skeleton, and spine_01 for UE4 skeleton, one socket for the electric guitar and another one for acoustic guitar;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To ensure proper functionality and alignment, please note that the character must be rigged to Epic skeleton - UE5 Skeleton , UE4 Skeleton.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The guitar meshes and textures used in this asset pack are provided by Epic Games and are included in the project. These assets are free to use in Unreal Engine projects under Epic’s terms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Showcase scene is not included&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatefishingmegapack"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatefishingmegapack"&gt;Ultimate Fishing Megapack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/77c0afbf3daa1da84c6af14c64fb8c28f4b9de1c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=aa74ba5b485bb073b18eba40f3e92e12"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our latest and greatest pack for you, is a fully original fishing pack. Containing almost 100 props this pack contains everything you need (and more) to populate your fishing village - with docks, boats, rigged and animated fish and all your fishing prop needs are included.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alongside all these fantastic items, Switchboard Studios, with the help of our lovely artists have made all the assets in this pack usable for any product. These assets are set up by default for First Person/VR games with a texel ratio as close to 10.24ppm as possible for all assets! No more down-ressing your assets to save on texture budgets and seeing all the lovely detail disappear - these assets are made to a AAA quality AND will hold up to the inevitable optimization pass.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Assets Included:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;The entire collection of assets in Fishing Docks &amp;amp; Boats Pack&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The entire collection of assets in Freshwater Fish Pack with Animations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;An entirely new collection of assets, including a large fishing boat with a collection of completely new assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;A fully modular dock and fishing set.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Over 50 props, including modular pieces and over 70 unique set dressing props.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;120fps example scene utilizing a Physically Based Lighting setup. (Disable the reflection plane for 120fps)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Every asset audited to be as close to 10.24ppm (First Person Quality)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sensibly made asset packing to reduce material calls on large amounts of items.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;7 rigged and animated fish&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Carp&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Catfish&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Large Mouth Bass&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Salmon&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Trout&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;White Fish&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Yellow Perch&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A fishing rod&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A fishing hat!&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Four basic animations to get you started&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A boat with interior, engine equipment, boxes and fish&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 95&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 84&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 236&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 128-4096&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hauntedprison"&gt;&lt;a id="hauntedprison" href="https://youtu.be/ELz_rOqMnhc"&gt;Haunted Prison&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Haunted Prison Environment with 118 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any kind of Virtual Production levels here is the pack that you get and use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;DISCLAIMER:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lumen enabled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Water Plugin needs to be enabled for the product functionality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;118 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 118 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 124&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 170&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hypertimemanagersystemv3"&gt;&lt;a id="hypertimemanagersystemv3" href="https://youtu.be/8s9a6LWQpDU"&gt;Hyper Time Manager System v3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyper Time Manager System v3&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Hyper Time Manager System v3 gives you full control over in-game time, allowing seamless synchronization between systems like NPC schedules, day-night cycles, and world events. I designed this system to help developers build immersive, time-aware gameplay mechanics that are both powerful and easy to integrate.It operates on a central time authority stored in the GameState, so all systems — from quests to environment — stay perfectly in sync.This system is also included in our Dynamic Weather &amp;amp; Sky system.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Interactive Time Manipulation&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Let players skip time by interacting with objects like beds, advancing to specific hours for pacing or immersion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;System Integration&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use flexible dispatchers to connect with your own systems (e.g., day-night cycle, NPC routines, environment changes)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Advanced Time Management&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define non-linear timelines, custom time scales, and dynamic schedules for time-based events&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Time Zones&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Assign unique time zones to regions of your world for added realism or gameplay contrast&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gamestate Time Authority&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The core system stores and syncs time centrally in the GameState, so other systems can bind to it and stay consistent&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;100% Blueprint, multiplayer-ready, modular, and fully customizable&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Future-proof design with ongoing updates&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Clean, well-documented Blueprints with clear naming&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Scalable systems for hobby to AAA-scale productions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cross-genre ready (Action-Adventure, Open-World, Co-op, Survival, Horror, RPG, FPS, TPS)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully network-replicated for multiplayer support&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Built for cross-platform use (tested on Windows)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Modular, component-based (drag-and-drop integration)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Data-driven setups using DataTables where applicable&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Blueprint-only implementation where practical&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for performance in multiplayer and large worlds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Trusted by developers across indie to large productions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="hyperoutlinerandsymbolsystemv3"&gt;&lt;a id="hyperoutlinerandsymbolsystemv3" href="https://youtu.be/7h2-kTsoagI"&gt;Hyper Outliner and Symbol System v3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyper Outliner and Symbol System v3&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Guide and inform your players with in-world outlines and symbols. Fully replicated, clean, and ready for multiplayer games.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Highlight interactables, enemies, objectives, and more — with dynamic symbols, distance-based visibility, and custom filters.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;No code needed. Works across Adventure, Co-op, Shooter, or Open-World games.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Also included within our flagship product MST Pro.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Explore all compatible Hyper systems or try the MST Pro demo to experience the Hyper ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Or buy directly from our official store — shop now, pay later available.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Key characteristics:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set an outliner on any actor from any place&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Uses an actor component with useful functions to manage your outlines easily&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Three different Colors Predefined&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;I've setup a primary, secondary and an third/other outliner.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Toggle multiple actors via function from the AC_Outliner&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Toggle Global scene depth easily&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set and attach a symbol on any of your actors. Like ? ! ⮟ Perfect for quest systems&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set options on the Symbols like:&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Play Rate&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rotation&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Up and Down Movement&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mesh&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Color sets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Future-proof design with ongoing updates&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Clean, well-documented Blueprints with clear naming&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Scalable systems for hobby to AAA-scale productions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cross-genre ready (Action-Adventure, Open-World, Co-op, Survival, Horror, RPG, FPS, TPS)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully network-replicated for multiplayer support&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Built for cross-platform use (tested on Windows)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Modular, component-based (drag-and-drop integration)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Data-driven setups using DataTables where applicable&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Blueprint-only implementation where practical&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for performance in multiplayer and large worlds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Trusted by developers across indie to large productions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="hyperfootstepsystemv3"&gt;&lt;a id="hyperfootstepsystemv3" href="https://youtu.be/p_2viNMyLFg"&gt;Hyper Footstep System v3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyper Footstep System v3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trigger synced footstep effects based on surface type, speed, and movement state. Works with any animation system.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes sounds, particles, decals, and multiplayer support. Modular, no code needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drop-in compatible with RPG, Shooter, Horror, and Survival projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also included within our flagship product MST Pro.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;This system is extensive, the core features are as follows:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Based on physical surfaces, switch footstep sounds and effects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes Wet footsteps trigger in shallow water&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Defined in an actor component so you can drag it on your character&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Works with auto landscape material, example included&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Triggered via Animation Notify, easy to set up.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Also works on non-humanoid characters.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Light, Moderate, and Heavy steps possible. For instance, a light character should spawn a different sound on grass than a heavy one. These sound variants are not included but it is easy to switch!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The most common surfaces are included in this project:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sand&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Grass&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stone&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Snow&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Wood&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Water&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;And a default surface layer for fallback if none is specified.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Future-proof design with ongoing updates&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clean, well-documented Blueprints with clear naming&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Scalable systems for hobby to AAA-scale productions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cross-genre ready (Action-Adventure, Open-World, Co-op, Survival, Horror, RPG, FPS, TPS)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully network-replicated for multiplayer support&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built for cross-platform use (tested on Windows)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular, component-based (drag-and-drop integration)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Data-driven setups using DataTables where applicable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blueprint-only implementation where practical&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for performance in multiplayer and large worlds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Trusted by developers across indie to large productions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="hypermeshtoiconcreatorv3"&gt;&lt;a id="hypermeshtoiconcreatorv3" href="https://youtu.be/kDe1UQNjw4w"&gt;Hyper Mesh to Icon Creator v3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyper Mesh to Icon Creator v3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Convert meshes into clean inventory icons with lighting, backgrounds, rotation, and transparency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fully local and fast. No Photoshop or render queue needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal for any game with inventory, vendors, or UI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect in combination with our flagship product MST Pro.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore all compatible Hyper systems or try the MST Pro demo to experience the Hyper ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Or buy directly from our official store — shop now, pay later available.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;This system comprises the following core features:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Generate Icon Textures from Static or Skeletal Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Save and Load your current configurations quicker generation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use a Datatable to configure which items you want to show in the icon generator and use shortcuts to toggle between meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Future-proof design with ongoing updates&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clean, well-documented Blueprints with clear naming&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Scalable systems for hobby to AAA-scale productions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cross-genre ready (Action-Adventure, Open-World, Co-op, Survival, Horror, RPG, FPS, TPS)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully network-replicated for multiplayer support&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built for cross-platform use (tested on Windows)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular, component-based (drag-and-drop integration)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Data-driven setups using DataTables where applicable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blueprint-only implementation where practical&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for performance in multiplayer and large worlds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Trusted by developers across indie to large productions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="carnivalenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="carnivalenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/LGg8NGMExgA"&gt;The Carnival Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you ready for a ghost-filled adventure in the horror-themed carnival environment? This package offers top-quality assets, textures, and animations for your amusement park, including a self-rotating carousel prepared with blueprints.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Carnival with 67 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes Showcased Preassembled Scene&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any kind of Virtual Production levels here is the pack that you get and use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;DISCLAIMER :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lumen enabled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lumen Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;67 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 67 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 93&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 156&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.2, 5.3 ,5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mysticdungeonenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="mysticdungeonenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/ZRLGV6CtLi4"&gt;Mystic Dungeon Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mystic Dungeon Environment with 52 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes Showcased Preassembled Scene&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any kind of Virtual Production levels, here is the pack that you can use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;DISCLAIMER:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This product supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lumen Documentation link.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lumen enabled. Includes nanite meshes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;52 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 52 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 41&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 98&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatelevelarttool"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatelevelarttool" href="https://youtu.be/muosdp29hKs"&gt;Ultimate Level Art Tool&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7a0c7487ddb3245f65f65e8b79284b0f1bcb962b.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=d3672600bd26c190c2a82174f80b93a0"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of being a leading art outsourcing company.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As an art outsourcing company, our primary focus has been delivering exceptional visual assets, animations, and art production services to game developers. However, recognizing the industry's evolving needs and the importance of efficient workflows, we have embarked on the development of our groundbreaking code plugin tool.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Under the hood, the Ultimate Level Art Tool has an impressive number of features. We are also planning to develop the tool further, expanding its functionality and versatility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate Level Art Tool has a lot of features :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a fully Modular Building with one tool&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create your custom mesh palette&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adjustable mesh snapping Modes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One-click material assigned to the collection&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One-click create a blueprint from the collection&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One-click Prop Duplication&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Place multiple modular meshes simultaneously&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a realistic simulated mesh groups&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quick workspace setup with drag-and-drop static mesh assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple modular placements simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Separate categories for modular and prop placement&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple material assignments for equivalent static mesh actors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to work on multiple structures simultaneously with the collection feature&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Code Modules UltimateLevelArtTool(Editor)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes 75&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints 23&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Network Replicated No&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trumpetandsaxanimations"&gt;&lt;a id="trumpetandsaxanimations" href="https://youtu.be/rvOVSkYC344"&gt;Trumpet &amp; Sax | Animations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Asset Pack Overview&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This asset pack contains a set of animation assets for Saxophone(9 anims) and two types of Trumpets(7 anims for each trumpet), designed for both UE5 and UE4 skeletons, perfect for casual or performance scenes involving a Sax/Trumpeter NPC.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;⚠️ Note:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Sax should be socketed on the right hand&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Trumpets shoudl be socketed on the left hand&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;To create your own sockets from scratch, follow the guitarist tutorial video and use the same process.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rigged to Epic Skeleton: Yes ( Manny UE5 , Mannequin UE4)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;If rigged to the Epic skeleton, IK bones are included: Yes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Number of Animations: 23&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Animation Types : In-place&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Compatibility:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions -&amp;nbsp;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="animatedfarmanimalsandfarmer-3dlowpolycubic"&gt;&lt;a id="animatedfarmanimalsandfarmer-3dlowpolycubic" href="https://youtu.be/jZjqior7Hfg"&gt;Animated Farm Animals &amp; Farmer- 3D LOW POLY Cubic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Animals - rigged models, animations&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Horse x3 , Cowx3, Bull x2, Goat x2, Sheep x2, Pig x1, Dog x2 , Cat x3, Hen x2, Rooster x2, Duck x3, 1 x Farmer man&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;24-28 animations for each animal&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;32 animation for Farmer&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Only eyes blink animations contain scale keys&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;One single simple texture&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Goat and Sheep share same skeleton and animations&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Cows and Bulls share same skeleton and animations&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Birds share same skeleton and animations&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Dogs share same skeleton and animations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="archvizinterior_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="archvizinterior_vol1"&gt;ArchViz Interior Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5a84f72f8d783e9cbb3769a3db0aff0f9825788e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=342829d52dd7e982db946f6ef0e5ebe3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greetings ! ️&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sunlight spills through elegant spaces, bringing warmth to every corner of this high-quality interior environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Designed for architectural visualization and immersive walkthroughs, this scene blends realism with rich detail perfect for modern homes, design showcases, or smart living projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every object tells a story crafted with care, optimized for performance, and ready to elevate your interior renders.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What’s Included:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;156 unique objects, from stylish sofas and textured carpets to smart home devices and cozy decor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple material variations for sofas and carpets customize effortlessly to match your design vision&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Interior lighting, electronics, books, kitchenware, fruits &amp;amp; vegetables, vases, wall panels, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All static meshes are vertex-optimized with efficient materials for use in both Archviz and games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A powerful Blueprint system with UI widget + 3-button actor to change materials in real-time great for interactive presentations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in mini-map system showing real-time player location within the scene&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got a question or need assistance? Feel free to contact us anytime at info@akairo.io we're here to help with technical support, suggestions, refunds, or any of your requests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;185 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedchristmastown"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedchristmastown" href="https://youtu.be/mE5Vi2WhojU"&gt;Stylized Christmas Town&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stylized Christmas Town&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stylized Christmas Town with 81 meshes. There are many different types of Assets to help you create or polish your Environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;FEATURES:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game-ready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game-ready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 81&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes [Automatically generated)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 59&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 130&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 2k, 4k&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bigslumalley"&gt;&lt;a id="bigslumalley"&gt;Big Slum Alley&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a3c60ea3d1b47fbaf2ee97dab8b69cf49b1ed5b9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8eb0f223f0deb0a964a3d8f3d7658fff"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greetings !&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Neon haze meets concrete decay in this gritty, atmospheric urban alley.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; From flickering signs to damp pavement and tangled wiring, every element is designed for immersive storytelling perfect for cyberpunk scenes, street markets, or dystopian backstreets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This is a place of contrast chaotic, vibrant, and brimming with urban tension.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inspired by Asian slums, this detailed environment features a rich network of alleys, layered architecture, neon signage, and urban clutter, crafted with deep care and realism. Whether you're building a cinematic walk-through or populating a game level, this pack delivers both character and flexibility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What’s Included:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Neon-lit signage (Street Food, Pubs, Discounts, and more) with a Blueprint system to customize and generate unique billboard variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular buildings, tangled pipes, vents, AC units, scaffolding, and street furniture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Urban debris, cracked roads, cardboard boxes, tangled wires, and graffiti&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Decals including dirt, water splashes, stains, and grime for environmental storytelling&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Wet surfaces, moody lighting setups, and volumetric fog for cinematic night scenes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Carefully optimized assets (low-poly models for UE4.27, Nanite support for selected walls/floors in UE5.0+)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Highly detailed meshes designed for close-up shots and high visual fidelity&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic modeling with extreme attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite support (UE5.0+) for selected walls and floors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blueprint-powered neon system for custom advertisements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demo map included use directly or build your own from modular elements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No characters included (demo video uses free Marketplace character for scale)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build your own urban labyrinth layered, dense, and pulsing with life.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; Got a question or need assistance? Feel free to contact us anytime at info@akairo.io we're here to help with technical support, suggestions, refunds, or any of your requests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="megapack_christmasdecorations"&gt;&lt;a id="megapack_christmasdecorations"&gt;MegaPack: Christmas Decorations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/53137346677170f8172f72254d71ecfeef99ca26.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7b047665776866bc315e15db10b99669"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greetings !✨&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beneath soft lights and snow-dusted windowsills, warmth flickers like a memory of home.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This holiday decoration set brings festive charm and cozy detail perfect for winter interiors, cheerful storefronts, celebration scenes, or romantic setups.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; It’s not just decor it’s atmosphere, nostalgia, and sparkle wrapped into one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now packed with even more joy this bundle combines both Warm Christmas and Valentine’s Day assets in one complete package.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What’s Included:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;114 high-quality, fully optimized 3D models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Christmas trees, garlands, wreaths, stockings, and twinkling lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gift boxes, ribbons, festive candles, bells, snow globes, and tableware&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Valentine's balloons with editable text, floral decor, chocolates, and themed accessories&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Carpets with parallax materials, drinks, and a wide variety of decorative items&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic models crafted with close attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Editable number balloons easily customize the text for any celebration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully optimized assets for smooth performance in games and Archviz&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comes in two separate UE versions: 4.27 and 5.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;UE5 version includes Lumen lighting for vibrant, real-time reflections and shadows&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building a magical Christmas morning, a heartfelt Valentine's setting, or a festive event scene this collection has everything you need to make it feel real.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got a question or need assistance? Feel free to contact us anytime at info@akairo.io we're here to help with technical support, suggestions, refunds, or any of your requests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;114 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 114 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 89&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 143&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3 ,5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="grandpalace_majesticmansionandluxuriousinteriorenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="grandpalace_majesticmansionandluxuriousinteriorenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/usb8xNptGTY"&gt;Grand Palace - Majestic Mansion and Luxurious Interior Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hey there, developer buddy! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Need a fancy, royal-style place for your next scene? I’ve found just the spot! This Grand Palace Environment Pack gives you a big, detailed mansion with elegant rooms, tall ceilings, and polished marble halls. It’s built for realism and fits smoothly into your Unreal Engine project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack includes two lighting setups: one for bright daytime scenes, and one for a warm, moody night. From graceful staircases to quiet sitting rooms, everything feels rich, calm, and lived-in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for cutscenes, story moments, or any project that needs a touch of luxury.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here’s what I packed for you:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Decorative fountains and garden features for outdoor charm&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Realistic food props: fruit bowls, bread, desserts, and plated meals&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Kitchen essentials: dishes, serving trays, cookware, and storage boxes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ A spacious main hall with marble floors and tall arched ceilings&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Rich, detailed mansion architecture with luxury finishes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ A cozy, book-filled library with shelves, reading chairs, and warm lighting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Classic candleholders, chandeliers, and wall sconces for ambient lighting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Landscaped exterior with hedges, stone paths, and trimmed lawns&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hey Buddy, Here's a Disclaimer:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make sure the HDRI Plugin is enabled to get everything running smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got a question or need assistance? Feel free to contact us anytime at support@barrelbark.com&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We're here to help with technical support, suggestions, refunds, or any of your requests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;434 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 434 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 906&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 1075&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylescape_ruins"&gt;&lt;a id="stylescape_ruins"&gt;Stylescape: Ruins&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/563a8569c6b6c3ed759629dbbe2e1425148ff211.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e1e033b88da5e42175cb9278272373fb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stylescape: Ruins, a new addition to the Stylescape family, is a fully modular kit with a stylized twist, featuring:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 174 modular meshes (all aligned to 10cm grid space)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Biome based materials for Forest(default), Snow, and Desert&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Procedural top layer based on mesh rotation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; PBR shaders utilizing AO, Roughness, Specular, and Normal&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 4k trim sheets for all structural pieces&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blueprint presets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Debris foliage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Decorative ivy&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: Does not contain nor require the base Stylescape kit such as: landscape and nature assets (trees, rocks, ferns, flowers)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: (Please include a full, comprehensive list of the features of the product)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;22 x Walls&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;32 x Ruined Walls&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;13 x Floors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 x Ruined Floors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;14 x Merged Floors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;6 x Pillars&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;6 x Ivy&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;8 x Blueprint Presets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 x Debris Foliage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Many others such as: Windows, Doorways, Wooden Pieces, Stairs, and Railings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Seasonal/Biome materials: Moss, Snow, &amp;amp; Sand&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4k Trim Sheets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 174&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, custom &amp;amp; auto generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vertex Count: 16 - 1,962&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 7 &amp;amp; 28&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 30&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 256, 512, 1024, 2048, 4096&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Documentation: None, but you could visit our Discord anytime you need support!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Important/Additional Notes: Does not contain the base Stylescape kit shown in the screenshots!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylescape_stylizedenvironmentkit"&gt;&lt;a id="stylescape_stylizedenvironmentkit" href="https://youtu.be/tRSrY0t-0Aw"&gt;Stylescape: Stylized Environment Kit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Latest Version: v1.6 | Video Update&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;UE5.5+ Update 4/6/25: Updated Demo, improved overall visuals, added bushes, new main level: Demo_Landmass&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;UE5 Update 7/8/22: Impostors are now back to high quality&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;UE5.1 Update 11/16/22: Enabled Nanite on grass, rocks, and landscape, updated Demo_RVT level.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;If you're looking for a much higher visual fidelity style with much more content check out Stylescape HD!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Stylescape is a highly flexible and optimized environment kit, built to utilize all of the latest UE4 and UE5 features such as Landmass, Water, Edit Layers, and Runtime Virtual Textures.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Landscape Auto Material with 2 auto slope layers, auto grass patches layer, 8 paintable layers, micro/macro tiling blending, and slope noise masks&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Latest version includes LAM version with texture normals and 3 extra layers for your own customizing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Full product support even for non-related questions, community Discord, and video tutorials that take you through the entire usage process&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Ground foliage (grass, flowers) are geometry based, which means nearly zero overdraw&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;All leaves and grass are vertex wind animated and comes with an extra customizable animated panning wave&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Assign any color for all leaves and grass, tutorial video available&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;All grass, trees, and rocks blend with landscape via optional RVT assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Trees have high quality 4k impostor billboards&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Easily add foliage to your level with included procedural foliage spawners&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Background mountain meshes with dynamic material to control slope angle and textures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Easy to place BP water actor with material and scaling controls, underwater fog, and distortion (or use Water actors)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Demo_Landmass map w/ Landmass mountains, Water plugin lakes &amp;amp; streams&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Requires water and landmass plugin&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LANDSCAPE AUTO MATERIAL -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Paintable layers: Grass, Evergreen, Dirt, Sand, Snow, 3 Extra, Remove Procedural&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Auto layers: Slope Dirt (Procedurally Tiled), Slope (World Aligned), Grass Patches&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Compatibility with landscape Edit layers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Noise masks for Slope layers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Noise mask for Grass layer&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Distant landscape fresnel&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Micro &amp;amp; Macro LOD texture tiling&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Grasstypes for all layers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Alternate cheaper version&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;EXTRA MATERIALS -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Underwater Fog &amp;amp; Distortion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;PostFX Sharpening&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cloud Shadows&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;MESHES -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;2 Grass, strip &amp;amp; cluster&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2 Flowers, single &amp;amp; cluster&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1 Fern&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2 Mushrooms, single &amp;amp; cluster&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;4 Large Rocks, 3 Rock Clusters&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;7 Trees: 2 Oaks &amp;amp; Tall Oak, Poplar, Short &amp;amp; Tall Spruce, Birch&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;3 Background Mountains&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1 Vintage Radio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;MISC -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Demo map showcasing Grassland, Evergreen, &amp;amp; Snow biomes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Foliage blending via landscape RVT&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Actor Blueprint w/ scaling &amp;amp; material controls&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Tree Impostors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Ground foliage distance "growing" effect&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 33&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, custom &amp;amp; auto generated&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vertex Count: 54 (Small Rock) - 6,692 (Background Mountains)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes w/ Impostors (Trees)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 18 Masters, 68 Instances&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 124&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 256 - 4096&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: PC&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Documentation: Stylescape Guide&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalvillageenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalvillageenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/vDZcnA5rMek"&gt;Medieval Village&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c9abcb984bed086300752c9eba97d461ca45bdd4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=eeaa543b501123c6eab19c12b886645f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Medieval Village – Rustic Fantasy Environment with 226 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes Showcased Preassembled Scene&lt;/p&gt