ws&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Window/Mac/PS4/Xbox&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="romanstatuespackvol1"&gt;&lt;a id="romanstatuespackvol1"&gt;Roman Statues Pack Vol 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8f6042d3e972fb332693c30311ea39529c4640bd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b0e089e5d4d04e71cdedbcea605435d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;11 Realistic High-Quality Roman Statues&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package provides eleven high-quality and well-optimized statues to populate your game environments or virtual production levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please create a ticket for all your promotional requests, technical support needs, suggestions, and refund requests.Number of Unique Meshes: 14&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials: 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 21&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K to 2K&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: No&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkbenches"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkbenches"&gt;Cyberpunk Benches&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1d761eead116d922c66329b811ff8bdb8891f52e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9551f3cec737122caac35158e00f9a43"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Benches with 10 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets and high-quality assets. It has a good level of detail and is optimized for Gameready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any Virtual Production levels, here is the pack you can use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;105 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 10 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 22&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 50&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkassaultrifles"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkassaultrifles"&gt;Cyberpunk Assault Rifles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5570a23bb8843d2c6153b4d4adcdb9988f13a673.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f2a4a4a6aad039f4bed3ec89d3355100"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Assault Rifles with 82 Unique Meshes. This includes all showcased assets, which are high-quality assets with a good level of detail and optimized for Game-Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** IMPORTANT NOTE: The asset pack has 82 Unique Meshes. 13 of them are complete weapons, and 69 are smaller parts of the guns. For instance, one of the complete weapons has a combined static mesh, and the handgrip, silencer, and sights have static meshes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any Virtual Production levels, here is the pack you can use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;82 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;128&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 57 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 77&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 213&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="militaryhelicopter_riggedandbpcontrollablewandskins"&gt;&lt;a id="militaryhelicopter_riggedandbpcontrollablewandskins"&gt;Military Helicopter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/250869694677ed2e9564863bb3382c6d4a987363.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f3ee8a09c3aed3ab48051303be693891"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Art was created in collaboration with Leartes and Dekogon Studios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animation and Blueprint setup by Leartes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Art by Dekogon Studios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pitch can be controlled by W key and S key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Steer can be controlled by A key and D key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Throttle can be controlled with E and Q key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Camera Rotation can be controlled by Mouse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;F and G Key - Open/Close Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Helicopter Materials are changeable in Detail Panel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Setup for easy drop and play&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom sounds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master Material to control features&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple Design Skins&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes static mesh version in addition to skeletal mesh and blueprint&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4K Texture Sets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control the majority of all props and models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="classicracecar"&gt;&lt;a id="classicracecar"&gt;Classic Race Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/04773865440261fcbcbdd28655151be5f73561a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9bc40827bb73b4d0d9067c0a14499872"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Classic Race Car Driveable / Animated / Realistic / Fully Customizable with separate Parts / Blueprints / Material Instances. There are Roughness / Metallic / Color parameters in material instances so you can arrange materials easily; the Vehicle will be in one blueprint and also six separate meshes, so you will be able to use them as you wish to create a prop for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Radio System Added&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All Sounds included.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Dirt / Edge Wears&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button Animating Car's Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 37&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fps4kcustommodernshotguns_vol2unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="fps4kcustommodernshotguns_vol2unrealengine"&gt;FPS 4K Custom Modern Shotguns - VOL.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/857ea5a7cdd2582bf4a7b22c207d870cb53de63d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4c7dbed510ab2329f6edcf45263dc1bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;(Set of 5) 4K Textured, Highly detailed custom designed modern first person shooter quality Shotguns&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes full gun assembled and individual gun parts - 53 Meshes total&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pre Assembled into Blueprint setup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High quality and fidelity texture sets - 4k Textures&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Uses only 1 material for single draw call per gun + Additional Glass Material for sights see through&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control the all the guns with instances for ease of changes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&