parate meshes, so you can use them to create props for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Video: https://youtu.be/ydGc7HynhoQ&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: This car is also included in our SUV Bundle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Documentation about how to use the car here&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SC_Doors sound plays with blueprint when pressing F, E, Q, R&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Dirt / Edge Wears&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button Animating Car's Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.19 , 4.20 , 4.21 , 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26+, 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxwarzone"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxwarzone"&gt;SFX Warzone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/31586966564c4ae17df78e7f9fb6608b896c17d5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4a620b9abcfd70dc26f12224bb5d1720"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;WW2 Warzone-themed Sound pack .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The product works with UE.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SFX packs Contains :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1 Ambience Sound Loop&lt;/li&gt;&lt