t;This course explores the engineering side of ML, from managing pipelines to deploying models in real-world environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore workflows for model deployment and monitoring Learn MLOps practices that ensure reliability at scale Automate processes for training, testing, and delivery Reinforce concepts with 10 structured exams&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Machine learning engineering connects research with real-world impact, ensuring that models remain accurate, scalable, and useful beyond experimentation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to bridge the gap between models and production systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="associatedataengineering_databasedesignandwarehousingwithpostgresqlandsnowflakewith10exams"&gt;&lt;a id="associatedataengineering_databasedesignandwarehousingwithpostgresqlandsnowflakewith10exams"&gt;Associate Data Engineering - Database Design and Warehousing with PostgreSQL &amp; Snowflake with 10 Exams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/53a4f3a89f638ff3e0b0fc524e7aafe559cc5389.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=02a8142ffbb97835224d21c74409df8c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Created by humans, supported with AI features like chat and quizzes, and verified by human editors for trustworthiness. Data needs structure before it can drive decisions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course introduces foundational skills in data engineering, focusing on database design and warehouse solutions with PostgreSQL and Snowflake as guiding platforms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Understand principles of relational database design Explore warehousing concepts for large-scale data storage Practice transformation and integration workflows Test your learning with 10 structured exams&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;By combining fundamentals with modern platforms, you’ll gain a versatile entry into data engineering practices that scale across industries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build the foundations of reliable and efficient data systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="profes