      <title>Paint like a Pro with Paintstorm, Realistic Paint Studio and Poser 12</title>
      <author>Graphixly LLC</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//software/paint-like-pro-with-paintstorm-realistic-paint-studio-and-poser-12</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">f40cb3e2f173c2eebcf7b250a420423a3b18793f</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Sep 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5dbcbf444513d876c3522f693637de2606da148f.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=268ebf6e194748940066bea97bc86963"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9e9ce62eb1390ef9a7ed0aec936485e7f6f7ba7b.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=616a06934cc691cfafe019248a6e776d"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Paint up a storm with great apps&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Level up your painting prowess with the elite creative tools in our all-new Paint Like a Pro Bundle. This epic collection of professional-quality software has everything you need to paint, model, render, and more. Leading the artistic charge is &lt;em&gt;Paintstorm Studio&lt;/em&gt; + &lt;em&gt;Paintstorm VIP Brushes&lt;/em&gt;—an indispensable toolkit of specially designed digital brushes and software for artists, created for projects of any complexity, genre, or technique. Rounding out the roster are &lt;em&gt;Realistic Paint Studio&lt;/em&gt; + VIP content, and &lt;em&gt;Poser&lt;/em&gt;, the 3D computer graphics program optimized for modeling detailed 3D figures. Pay what you want for these powerful creative platforms and help support No Kid Hungry with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $25 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#painstormstudio"&gt;Paintstorm Studio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#realisticpaintstudioplusvipcontent"&gt;Realistic Paint Studio + VIP content&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#paintstormstudiovipbrushes"&gt;Paintstorm Studio VIP Brushes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#poser12"&gt;Poser 12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#posercontent"&gt;Poser Content&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $25 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="painstormstudio"&gt;&lt;a id="painstormstudio" href="https://youtu.be/KPMmh1Zp1nc"&gt;Paintstorm Studio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Paintstorm Studio is an indispensable tool for artists, created for works of any complexity, genre and technique. Our goal was to create an intuitive, simple-to-use but at the same time functionally powerful tool that brings the process of digital painting to a new level, making it as comfortable as possible.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticpaintstudioplusvipcontent"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticpaintstudioplusvipcontent" href="https://youtu.be/5DJ8IBxojQk"&gt;Realistic Paint Studio + VIP content&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Realistic Paint Studio is a unique digital art software. The program combines the simplicity of traditional tools and pioneering innovations in digital art. No special education is required to work in Realistic Paint Studio. The interface is designed to show a familiar art station with real paper, brushes, pencils, pens, and markers, etc. instead of a complicated and hard-to-understand graphic editor.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="paintstormstudiovipbrushes"&gt;&lt;a id="paintstormstudiovipbrushes"&gt;Paintstorm Studio VIP Brushes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/df55ef90cc0623feb664948b5d265100000a295f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c8e7f9ec1591e5e2276a37829d1b0bb0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Paintstorm Studio VIP Brushes pack is a professionally designed brush pack. These brushes were created for use in Paintstorm Studio. There are over 65 brushes in this pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="poser12"&gt;&lt;a id="poser12" href="https://youtu.be/BAHUWa__aTQ"&gt;Poser 12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Premier 3D Rendering &amp;amp; Animation Software&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Easily create art and animation with 3D characters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Poser is a 3D computer graphics program optimized for 3D modeling of human figures. It is known for enabling digital artists to easily produce 3D animations and digital images, as well as the extensive availability of third-party digital content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="posercontent"&gt;&lt;a id="posercontent"&gt;Poser Content&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e6eb2efd5f06fa3afa5aab911391f6e665507d3c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d0e383b1e32f7fed3bf8a4670239f278"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;With Poser's Content, human and animal models are prepared for you to start designing and posing immediately. Figures are pre-rigged so artists can click-and-drag to pose body parts, sculpt faces, or create ethnic varieties. Thousands of poses, morphs, clothing, hair, materials, and accessories are included. Whether you create for interactive media, animation or the web, there’s always a need to integrate the human form. Poser delivers the power of interactive 3D figure design, offering infinite opportunities to portray human diversity, form and expression. Design with the human form for art, illustration, animation, comics, web, print, education, medical visualization, games, storyboarding, pre-visualization and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
