;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#medievalprops_vol1_barrels"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 1 - Barrels&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#muzzleflash3d"&gt;Muzzle Flash 3D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#interactionsystemx"&gt;Interaction System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#medievalprops_vol3_weaponrack"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 3 - Weapon Rack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#medievalprops_vol4_woodenchests"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 4 - Wooden Chests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bulletimpactdecals_vol1_concrete"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 1 - Concrete&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bulletimpactdecals_vol2_metal"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 2 - Metal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bulletimpactdecals_vol3_wood"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 3 - Wood&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ultimatespellsystem"&gt;Ultimate Spell System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#openworldaimultiplayerspawnsystem"&gt;Open World AI Multiplayer Spawn System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#firearmsevolved"&gt;Firearms Evolved&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#customizablebodycamcomponent"&gt;Customizable Bodycam Component&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#elitesoldiers"&gt;Elite Soldiers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#carfirefxvdb"&gt;Car Fire FX VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zombie_hazmat"&gt;Zombie - Hazmat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zomtechlite_aizombie"&gt;ZomTech Lite - AI Zombie&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#openworldaudiosystem"&gt;Open World Audio System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dystopiantank"&gt;Dystopian Tank&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#auraniagarafx"&gt;Aura Niagara FX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#customar-15stylerifle"&gt;Custom AR-15 Style Rifle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#skilltreesystemx"&gt;Skill Tree System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#customizedpostapocalypticcharacters"&gt;Customized Post Apocalyptic Characters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#groundvortexvdb"&gt;Ground Vortex VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zombie_police"&gt;Zombie - Police&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#levelingsystemx"&gt;Leveling System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fighterspack"&gt;Fighters Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#blazingorbsvdb"&gt;Blazing Orbs VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zombie_construction"&gt;Zombie - Construction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#characterstatsx"&gt;Character Stats X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#oldgangster"&gt;Old Gangster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#medievalprops_vol2_tents"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 2 - Tents&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#knight01templar"&gt;Knight 01 (Templar)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zombie_priest"&gt;Zombie - Priest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fantasyhero"&gt;Fantasy Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#medievalprops_vol5_torchesandbraziers"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 5 - Torches &amp; Braziers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="samurai_bugrimovmaksim"&gt;&lt;a id="samurai_bugrimovmaksim" href="https://youtu.be/hYrxkOHbR8U"&gt;SAMURAI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/83d1e422a11f23ba28c150c4b2ea9058aa241aeb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6d7893132fbd03241e72e607bd520c8c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5f4c90b7-a282-45fc-89df-61468afc867b"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring the history of Japan to your game with this detailed Samurai warrior. Customize your army with interchangeable helmets and a dynamic flag.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a modular character with 2 different helmet options to create unique warriors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comes equipped with 2 katanas.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="firefxvdb"&gt;&lt;a id="firefxvdb" href="https://youtu.be/LGqDDFCgsVU"&gt;Fire FX VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9c92e1e07846e21d66f576947568fbd4f7f5f00c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=33695e2d6030aaff35ccf5fb21213094"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/8ba5d959-cc53-48ef-91e9-20912bb82f8e"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Bring warmth and destruction to your environments with this versatile collection of 13 realistic, volumetric fire effects suitable for any scene.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;13 Fire effects using heterogeneous volumes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Color and density controls with Material Instances&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Dynamic ember and particle lighting to cast realistic light onto your environment.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Drag-and-drop, they're ready for immediate use.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="bulletimpactdecals_vol4_plaster"&gt;&lt;a id="bulletimpactdecals_vol4_plaster"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 4 - Plaster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7871b10edc105df61836b3101b1a3d39ff810a0b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9ecdd6f991bc725e88d43c0b2424f39b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/88fb6aac-8aeb-443e-8d18-fdc1774a5f7c"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Crumble your interior walls with high-quality, realistic bullet damage. This pack uses parallax occlusion mapping to create convincing depth and detail in every crack. Drag, drop, and transform your scenes with dynamic bullet holes for a new level of immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parallax Occlusion Mapping, creating true depth and self-shadowing for ultra-realistic impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easily customize decal coloring and adjust the intensity of the parallax depth effect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simply drag and drop the decals into your scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="policeman_bugrimovmaksim"&gt;&lt;a id="policeman_bugrimovmaksim" href="https://youtu.be/JUekv9pTRcE"&gt;Policeman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5ffbc50fc7d3705d8a7a836d7da967f6733a7126.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ed6cb02cffcb3da9970fae14da375a8a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/f513d370-4187-4731-8091-d4e36302b0da"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add a high-quality, modern law enforcement officer to your project. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a modular character with multiple head options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comes equipped with a police shield and baton.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes integrated physics for realistic reactions to impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="bulletimpactdecals_vol5_highimpact"&gt;&lt;a id="bulletimpactdecals_vol5_highimpact"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 5 - High Impact&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9ac28f384ffffbd4223018ccf1f394f0dc8dc7c6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a1a7b16abeb6d065806e7ba0d35081cd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/d6c781c1-8e2c-4dc7-aad2-f2c2659c97ce"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Deliver devastating damage with the High Impact bullet decal pack. This pack uses parallax occlusion mapping for convincing depth, perfect for heavy caliber weapons or explosive shrapnel. Drag, drop, and transform your scenes for a new level of immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parallax Occlusion Mapping, creating true depth and self-shadowing for ultra-realistic impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easily customize decal coloring and adjust the intensity of the parallax depth effect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simply drag and drop the decals into your scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="hideandseekai"&gt;&lt;a id="hideandseekai" href="https://youtu.be/Us8CkNEYog8"&gt;Hide and Seek AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f1c032c649cdc58dea1af78c74bcfbe6ead9a0b8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e75e0a9559ee87e1b2229b9c6963fc20"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/2f9e5165-fb06-487a-85ec-e5dfa89d9648"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This kit is designed to immerse players in thrilling hide-and-seek scenarios, complete with an advanced AI system.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;If the AI loses track of the player, it will start searching for them in the location where it last saw them.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Upon spotting the player, it starts chasing them.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The AI interacts with lockers.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The AI patrols at designated points.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;If the AI hears something, it goes to the location of the sound. If the player makes a noise while inside a locker and the AI isn't close enough, it will inspect the area around the locker.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;It walks to random locations if the patrol mode is set to None.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The player can hide in the locker&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="predictivedefenseturret"&gt;&lt;a id="predictivedefenseturret" href="https://youtu.be/Dajs4g8bImE"&gt;Predictive Defense Turret&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d660c8ecb92119d63177d6160593007a9795ff88.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=422163e729485d78243063fe37b8c106"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/9c3a7ea5-47b8-4f00-b711-71080839685d"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Check out all pack reviews and questions on Orbital Market!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Interception Turret Actor&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Interception Component&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Interception Function Library&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Moving Target Dummy Actor&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Meshes, VFX, and SFX for Turret and Target actor.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="advancedplacementsystem"&gt;&lt;a id="advancedplacementsystem" href="https://youtu.be/jN3jW79ufuc"&gt;Advanced Placement System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f4a798d5d26bc76b1658bee9afeb3d5cbc17e9b5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8e16d02afce29205b676708037e8984e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/6cb15549-61b3-43f9-834f-bb5a720e0b37"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Elevate your projects with Advanced Placement System.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Data-Driven Management&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiplayer Replication&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Surface Recognition&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Snap to Object / Grab Objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;User Friendly Setup&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;100% Blueprint&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="parasitespack"&gt;&lt;a id="parasitespack" href="https://youtu.be/O4z5wnClTPA"&gt;Parasites Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b03c8881230f6bd3a88192a07cc73e79514edbd1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=92670452a3aeaa7b5ba8c9e77474c861"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/536252d1-3137-49fb-bfd8-67ce42dd9650"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash a horde of creatures with the Parasites Pack, a set of five unique, game-ready monsters complete with animations and sounds.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;A collection of 5 unique parasite characters.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; Fully animated with 59 animations.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sound Effects to bring the creatures to life.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Scaled and fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalprops_vol1_barrels"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalprops_vol1_barrels"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 1 - Barrels&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ecd37d0763ef8b12054548e5ffd63495656872b7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=542bba5a692d916087387976d2cfeb35"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/d7045bc7-ee60-484d-ac46-6cbc96e2cd1e"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Populate your scenes with this essential collection of wooden barrels. Perfect for adding detail to taverns, docks, alleyways, or battle-damaged environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 Unique Intact Wooden Barrels&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 Unique Broken Wooden Barrels&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality, optimized models ready to drop into any scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Customization options with versatile materials and instances to allow for quick changes to color and texture.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="muzzleflash3d"&gt;&lt;a id="muzzleflash3d" href="https://youtu.be/I_rQggKcl7g"&gt;Muzzle Flash 3D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/50f719a8928166fb8b26a16ce9b00eedb5a9e1d8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cd5b1a757d4d6a747da42120f936aee6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5cbcbcfa-8d17-4ed2-b0f1-9f9d96d95ba1"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elevate your firearms with this pack of dynamic muzzle effects. Built in Niagara, these flashes look realistic from any viewpoint.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;20 Niagara systems (11 Modern and 9 Futuristic variations for a variety of weapons).&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Muzzle flashes are volumetric and look correct from all angles.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Easy customization of scale, color, and intensity.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="interactionsystemx"&gt;&lt;a id="interactionsystemx" href="https://youtu.be/hnAPkpL8Yno"&gt;Interaction System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4c3f5d682b38b2e8c016225996817890ee46f1ba.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=18ab4c4991ca7d3531e34343eeaa76fe"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5fe41be5-e6af-482f-b784-b57341d2ea65"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Interaction System X is an advanced and flexible system designed to handle a wide variety of interactions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Interaction Types&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3D Widget&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Health&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Foliage Interaction&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Static Mesh Interaction&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Data Table&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quick Integration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Replicated&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Animated&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalprops_vol3_weaponrack"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalprops_vol3_weaponrack"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 3 - Weapon Rack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7100019a4964c435ee71fdb191315793a9451421.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=22f7990cb12170cbe022a4b37fc71000"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/da7b6d2c-9f6d-4fa7-b48c-4a7d1669c450"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Equip your armories and training grounds with this fully-stocked weapon rack set. This collection is perfect for adding to barracks, blacksmiths, or combat practice areas.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully-Stocked Weapon Rack including a rack, shield, spear, sword, bow, large axe, and small axe.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A classic straw-stuffed training dummy is also included.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality, optimized models ready to drop into any scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Customization options with versatile materials and instances to allow for quick changes to color and texture.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalprops_vol4_woodenchests"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalprops_vol4_woodenchests"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 4 - Wooden Chests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/442650200b3869c24418ed86a0e78a6ee60e24a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ddf9b1188cfbcb08aa8ca09c3d241fcc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/af0cae83-3996-40ef-b628-3e37254d102b"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Safeguard your treasure with this collection of classic wooden chests. Perfect for loot drops, storage props, or decorating a castle treasury.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;2 Wooden Chest variations, including both a large and a small wooden chest.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes Blueprints for easy interactive use.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Each chest has separate static meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Customization options with versatile materials and instances to allow for quick changes to color and texture.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="bulletimpactdecals_vol1_concrete"&gt;&lt;a id="bulletimpactdecals_vol1_concrete"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 1 - Concrete&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/24ca0c157f2b5e73c76dc5ed472e1dad44c4c661.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8b7428accb84fa0e4d64c9ac9bbedbd0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/500684fb-7191-4be5-a52e-224459929fdd"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shatter your concrete surfaces with high-quality, realistic bullet damage. This pack uses parallax occlusion mapping to create convincing depth and detail in every crater. Drag, drop, and transform your scenes with dynamic bullet holes for a new level of immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parallax Occlusion Mapping, creating true depth and self-shadowing for ultra-realistic impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easily customize decal coloring and adjust the intensity of the parallax depth effect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simply drag and drop the decals into your scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="bulletimpactdecals_vol2_metal"&gt;&lt;a id="bulletimpactdecals_vol2_metal"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 2 - Metal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2c86cca2b309158dbf177b53b9518c29f826f3ab.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a2f08471d8a3a204c9bfe3d440ae1136"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/6e5b626b-9a4a-465b-b987-f2c269bbfe2d"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shred your metal surfaces with high-quality, realistic bullet damage. This pack uses parallax occlusion mapping to create convincing depth in every piercing impact. Drag, drop, and transform your scenes with dynamic bullet holes for a new level of immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parallax Occlusion Mapping, creating true depth and self-shadowing for ultra-realistic impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easily customize decal coloring and adjust the intensity of the parallax depth effect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simply drag and drop the decals into your scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="bulletimpactdecals_vol3_wood"&gt;&lt;a id="bulletimpactdecals_vol3_wood"&gt;Bullet Impact Decals Vol. 3 - Wood&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/18293addfba68c38d3b3e414f9df6d2ec2648d81.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d69b0c6520149e2e0c7544c93d5280e5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/7ea47ff4-f53b-42fa-928b-13913b82e571"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Splinter your wooden environments with high-quality, realistic bullet damage. This pack uses parallax occlusion mapping to create convincing depth and detail in every chip. Drag, drop, and transform your scenes with dynamic bullet holes for a new level of immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parallax Occlusion Mapping, creating true depth and self-shadowing for ultra-realistic impacts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easily customize decal coloring and adjust the intensity of the parallax depth effect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simply drag and drop the decals into your scene.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatespellsystem"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatespellsystem" href="https://youtu.be/Rs-bTWW8O8A"&gt;Ultimate Spell System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f15aed5e196ba4532765dd60d5df33df7bac53ab.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1de0e74b55677e371d890c76dbb1df5b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/7bac6c72-ba72-4ca2-891e-9b8970dd3277"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; The "Ultimate Spell System" is an advanced magic system that enriches your gameplay with dynamic and exciting elements.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cooldown system&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;One Simple Component&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Casting spells system&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Charging Effect&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Setting animations for each spell&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A widget displaying health and mana, all spells, and their cooldowns&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Single and multiplayer support&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;6 sample spells&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;7 sample character animations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="openworldaimultiplayerspawnsystem"&gt;&lt;a id="openworldaimultiplayerspawnsystem" href="https://youtu.be/eGnKP_Vy8YA"&gt;Open World AI Multiplayer Spawn System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a20e9337e78ff10e4441826cec83934c611e4135.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=44277f83fa45b8452adf89dbcfcc8d0a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/819fbad0-fb85-4dd5-8276-15a098830f1f"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.17 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; If you are working on a single player open world game I suggest you get the single player pack instead.Check out all pack reviews and questions on Market!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;A spawn and de-spawn system perfect for open world or co-op games.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Everything is done server side and is designed from the ground up for multiplayer games.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Also works with dedicated servers.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Example AI. (Friendly and basic zombie AI)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Well documented Blueprints and easy to expand upon with your own variables and or settings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="firearmsevolved"&gt;&lt;a id="firearmsevolved" href="https://youtu.be/deF6V6vpFmo"&gt;Firearms Evolved&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/39b26ae691a42d22a1f97a17be4cfdcfb2d2fcd0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f5d8af1a78b8d024ff494ab7f0e19bb9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/4d741479-7751-4f0c-adb7-d6f44a55910a"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Check out all pack reviews and questions on Orbital Market!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firearm Blueprint&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firearm Variations (Rifle, Pistol, Shotgun)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Target Dummy&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reserves Component (Stores Ammunition)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Basic FPS Movement Component&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gym and Demo Level&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firearm Meshes and Animations (Imported from Lyra)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VFX: Bullet Tracer, Muzzle Flash, Bullet Impact&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="customizablebodycamcomponent"&gt;&lt;a id="customizablebodycamcomponent" href="https://youtu.be/JMXe4Ee3e4I"&gt;Customizable Bodycam Component&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/352435f4c648467f7aecf3f02bb9691f232aea5a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0ff700efc2a00aec1349812f434ebe5a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/3a8cb3f1-32a7-452d-a313-b46895a2d476"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Ultra Realistic Feeling &amp;amp; Ultra Customizable &amp;amp; Ultra Easy to Setup!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Realistic Bodycam Feeling&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Smooth Rotation&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Realistic Flashlight&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Zoom In/Out&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;ULTRA Customizable VHS Overlay&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;ULTRA Customizable VHS Effects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Customizable Bodycam Frame&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Walk/Run/Idle Camera Shakes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Landing Camera shake&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Exposed Material Parameters&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;100% Blueprint&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Easy to Use, Easy to Set Up!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="elitesoldiers"&gt;&lt;a id="elitesoldiers" href="https://youtu.be/hFe3KoH8FIQ"&gt;Elite Soldiers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bdfa307c76a7701870471635b655576593520592.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d54c3e18117d429dd53f1bae8701618c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/f59c8a3b-91f9-4a9a-b570-e935afdd093e"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Elite Soldier pack is a comprehensive asset for your next project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Soldier with multiple head options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes an automatic rifle, drone, and a dog assistant.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Variety of backpacks, with different weapon options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Character is rigged to the Epic skeleton for UE4 and UE5.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="carfirefxvdb"&gt;&lt;a id="carfirefxvdb" href="https://youtu.be/KHJBcPCF7U4"&gt;Car Fire FX VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ad8b8a3d4d7922493a2a92c12a07d11e248640ff.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=19b0a7db90fcde3b5bf63e090a30146f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/bc66a606-4617-47fc-9d89-d7a240844198"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Ignite your scenes with the Car Fire FX VDB pack, a collection of 10 realistic, volumetric fire effects ready to drag-and-drop into any project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;10 Car Fire effects using heterogeneous volumes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fire color and density controls in Blueprints and Material Instances.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag-and-Drop ready for immediate use.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dynamic Lighting to cast realistic, flickering firelight onto your environment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="zombie_hazmat"&gt;&lt;a id="zombie_hazmat"&gt;Zombie - Hazmat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c9eb5250cd30a3feaa86af1d95f17345cdf6b042.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=600c730d5742a1e6453186b83012a013"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/bc66a606-4617-47fc-9d89-d7a240844198"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Introduce a terrifying biohazard threat to your project with the Hazmat Zombie. Once a frontline responder, this character is now a walking nightmare, perfect for any post-apocalyptic or sci-fi horror setting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged to Epic skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game Ready &amp;amp; Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Textures &amp;amp; Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;IK Bones Included&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="zomtechlite_aizombie"&gt;&lt;a id="zomtechlite_aizombie" href="https://youtu.be/NMQ4B2l754A"&gt;ZomTech Lite - AI Zombie&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/392fe1b75d928b823809f3d01c2ec83d521c1f8c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1b8b6274ad2fa6f269852aac7404542e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/bae5f08a-25cb-496b-8891-5e856785e627"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; ZomTech Lite is a versatile asset perfect for creating zombie games. It offers a simple menu interface and advanced AI features for zombies that will significantly enhance your game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiplayer: Full support for multiplayer mode.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimization: The asset is optimized for smooth performance.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Grass Interaction: Simple interaction that works and is visible only to the owner of the pawn.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Basic Player Locomotion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pistol Shooting, Aiming&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stamina, Health&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Menu, Server browser, Host&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Map selection&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy to use&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="openworldaudiosystem"&gt;&lt;a id="openworldaudiosystem" href="https://youtu.be/20MimZJmYiM"&gt;Open World Audio System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/09b7503d17e55d9bc2581f8c7aa8d26ccdda4fdf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=460a279ee41f062c8a74d1545f17b0b7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/3dc8efb5-0b13-4925-a8cb-2ff052281298"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.19 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Check out all pack reviews and questions on Orbital Market!A system designed to make it easy to add ambient sounds and music to your level.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quickly add sound areas to your open world level.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Choose your own exploration, tension and combat music per area.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Choose your own ambient sounds and random ambient sounds per area.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change the music/ambient together with the time of day.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change the ambient when going in Interiors.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Easy to read and expand upon!&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;All logic is run on the client but works in a multiplayer game.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Well documented Blueprints and easy to expand upon with your own variables and settings.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;(Basic player character and Zombie AI are also there for demo purposes)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="dystopiantank"&gt;&lt;a id="dystopiantank" href="https://youtu.be/Ot2BwXkeIQM"&gt;Dystopian Tank&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e0e171d2dd1b6a3bb989b5fcabf4a660a0f5dfe2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b049e49dcc3bbf10f65e14f466c55ab2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/4eba1905-5d60-406d-9cce-5fd5b2d2f161"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This versatile tank, complete with a rotating turret and dual muzzles, is the perfect addition for your space, adventure, or fantasy game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes dual muzzles, rotating turret, and a backlight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully rigged for dynamic movement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;31 animations, including flight, rotation, and firing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 different materials to customize the tank's appearance.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="auraniagarafx"&gt;&lt;a id="auraniagarafx" href="https://youtu.be/n69pZ51BPdI"&gt;Aura Niagara FX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/de95defb1b38e7ccbc8c8293237b301c396ce839.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=16874a5886dfe84c6abe3c7de592eeb8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/b4397e94-a2f2-45fe-b09a-604acc7c6f87"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.26 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Power up your characters with Aura Niagara FX, a collection of 15 dynamic aura effects. These looping auras are perfect for showcasing special abilities, status effects, and magical buffs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;15 Aura Niagara systems, versatile use across any genre.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;7 Niagara Emitters for easy customization and control.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Effects are set to local space to ensure they seamlessly follow your character's movements.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All FX are optimized and loop continuously for smooth performance.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="customar-15stylerifle"&gt;&lt;a id="customar-15stylerifle"&gt;Custom AR-15 Style Rifle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/db59ef306497337695568980a5b3e391c2852708.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=21a916fec74ec1ad0e7baf9bbfd2a58a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/92d9abc7-4028-4b2a-98ea-4c78a8af0e66"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Elevate your project with this high-quality, game-ready model of a custom AR-15 rifle. This realistic model can be seamlessly integrated into your projecr, perfect for shooter, survival, or military games, or as a high-quality, detailed prop for cinematic renders. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality PBR textures for stunning, realistic detail up close.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a functional, easy to use rig for essential animations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demo set up with Epic's Animation Starter Pack.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="skilltreesystemx"&gt;&lt;a id="skilltreesystemx" href="https://youtu.be/M4aohc4YhuA"&gt;Skill Tree System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fbdd0355c2cddc9706258537a19b949022e794c7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0cca9cfe29d1035fe29a1bd303665fee"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/b8f7ae43-8637-4aa1-aa39-bcedb8d003a3"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Empower players to embark on personalized skill advancement journeys within your game world with Skill Tree System X.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set requirements for upgrading a particular skill.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Change the style, set frames, line colors, frame/widget size.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize skill points earned per level.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set the size of the board.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create multiple categories, such as perks, technology, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add decorations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Data Table&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Filling a data table using the EUW_Fill_DataTable tool&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Auto Save&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy to use&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="customizedpostapocalypticcharacters"&gt;&lt;a id="customizedpostapocalypticcharacters" href="https://youtu.be/RCD65lypB4k"&gt;Customized Post Apocalyptic Characters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6aad4d294f090ec60af70d37d36a0096453132ce.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8fa713c6d5668dd09bb36ee13c93ea2d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/2f9e8f01-d369-4d32-939a-e22f4d3d60e8"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create unique survivors with this highly customizable Post-Apocalyptic Character set, perfect for any desolate wasteland adventure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully customizable, including 3 heads, 5 pants options, 5 clothing types, 5 shoe styles, 5 backpacks, 3 hats, and 12 different masks.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;8 weapon types including a sniper rifle, rifle, 2 guns, knife, bita, ice axe, and star axe &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with the standard Epic Skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="groundvortexvdb"&gt;&lt;a id="groundvortexvdb" href="https://youtu.be/plQMlO0XZzk"&gt;Ground Vortex VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1e4b6ffe42318663fd32341307b2887e21998698.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=91fa40ded69b01aa37baebbb97fd70b1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/41c13f6f-21a4-40c4-9c2b-3d64da8dcf4f"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Unleash powerful ground-based magic with the Ground Vortex VDB pack. This collection features four cinematic, volumetric vortex effects perfect for spells, impacts, and environmental hazards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 unique ground vortex effects using heterogeneous volumes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Each vortex plays an animation with 480 frames. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color and density controls with Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Now includes additional Native VDB files!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="zombie_police"&gt;&lt;a id="zombie_police"&gt;Zombie - Police&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8ba75bf99facea58b2b043b15bb4810799ff4c61.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ab9e00b2b8b58efb08e100ef9bbbd7fb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/0a7a3a30-49fa-41bc-820b-d38cd068eadf"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The law has fallen, and it's coming for you. This Zombie Police Officer brings a chilling sense of urban decay and lost authority to any apocalyptic world, making for an unforgettable enemy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged to Epic skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game Ready &amp;amp; Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Textures &amp;amp; Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;IK Bones Included&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="levelingsystemx"&gt;&lt;a id="levelingsystemx" href="https://youtu.be/z1SNvYzr6aQ"&gt;Leveling System X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/eff527b786a77ae632dbcaaaaeb24d32e4378435.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5a0ffa96342ae5dd642f2d7daeda515f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/d84e11f8-5c6c-4bdb-9f9f-14be4d326626"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; "Leveling System X" is an innovative leveling system in gaming that revolutionizes the traditional method of gaining experience and character advancement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiplayer Support&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rank System&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Visualization of the Experience&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Leveling&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Visible Level, Rank, and Player Name&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level-Up Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sharing experience among players (the one dealing more damage receives more experience)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pool Manager&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="fighterspack"&gt;&lt;a id="fighterspack" href="https://youtu.be/lWzUM7KcUTw"&gt;Fighters Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/019c92bf75621706c2097ad8028dcbd9bcaccf50.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=24cbd98d44422f87fc4a3540c3288616"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/53f4eb85-54c9-4760-835b-13c80a6420a2"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Populate your project with a diverse roster of combatants from the Fighters Pack, featuring a variety of styles perfect for any fighting game or action title.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;15 Unique Fighters, each with a unique design.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with the Epic Skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="blazingorbsvdb"&gt;&lt;a id="blazingorbsvdb" href="https://youtu.be/2V8ZDXC2jRg"&gt;Blazing Orbs VDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/81b266f26d3f927c4542e905109ad6094cc8d23f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=410f10bdb5768b22e9bd35c6bef0e16f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/d6093be3-2cb2-47ce-a892-feb2c9ab7479"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.3 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Add a touch of magic and mystique to your project with Blazing Orbs VDB. This pack contains 9 abstract, volumetric energy orbs, ideal for projectiles, magical artifacts, or ambient effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;9 Abstract effects using heterogeneous volumes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color and density controls with Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dynamic Lighting to cast realistic, colored light onto your environment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag-and-drop, they're ready for immediate use.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="zombie_construction"&gt;&lt;a id="zombie_construction"&gt;Zombie - Construction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2fdae7a7aa84a41eb44bcd56658d296c9bfee3ca.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4748f44fefd12dcf639346894efb17c2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/8821feaa-88b5-4887-b27f-190fdfaf6012"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a more terrifying world with the Zombie Construction Worker. His instantly recognizable high-visibility gear adds a grounded, everyday horror to your environment, making him a staple threat.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged to Epic skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game Ready &amp;amp; Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Textures &amp;amp; Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;IK Bones Included&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="characterstatsx"&gt;&lt;a id="characterstatsx" href="https://youtu.be/fhujtwb9y3k"&gt;Character Stats X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/09ddbbd54046b4f236aaac3f10d0b753ad609b20.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=addcdef404d5bed4633a723567de754a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/2f24b68a-23a1-4de4-bd5e-f55097518b39"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; "Character Stats X" is a comprehensive character statistics system designed to enhance the gaming experience.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;User-friendly&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Nice design&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Stats: oxygen, health, hunger, thirst, stomach, intestine, bladder, energy, mental health, stamina&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fast integration&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;4 animations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="oldgangster"&gt;&lt;a id="oldgangster" href="https://youtu.be/DaBJ0iL7674"&gt;Old Gangster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9fbf62640d9e5d0732761fe247d2c4280eccf774.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5c78127a71e0b483dabed8cd20e6b35d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/0f896299-3dbd-447d-93b1-98da85ea2f81"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introduce the "Old Gangster" to your detective or adventure game. This character comes equipped with a submachine gun and is ready for integration into your game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully customizable with a variety of outfits to suit any theme.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes basic facial morphs for added expression.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a Submachine gun&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalprops_vol2_tents"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalprops_vol2_tents"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 2 - Tents&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/55b2325d31f73f67a8b5ba14c2102bbc85243e95.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b09dd92808f02a2eee152e397170c355"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create immersive encampments with this essential collection of medieval tents and sleeping gear. Perfect for soldier camps, adventurer resting spots, or outlaw hideouts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 Unique Tent Models, including large, medium, and small tent variations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comes with a versatile bedroll/sleeping bag prop.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Customization options with a versatile base material and 3 demo instances to allow for quick changes to color and texture.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="knight01templar"&gt;&lt;a id="knight01templar" href="https://youtu.be/dRrMfgP_zU8"&gt;Knight 01 (Templar)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/599798b2c3d38d59332ac879970322f3f5dab2e1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a0be3f7db610101e27a4e852c506b16c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/a102a4ab-7058-40f6-84d8-64050d7f85ab"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring the valiant Templar Knight into your world. This customizable character is battle-ready with a selection of weapons and features dynamic cloth simulation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully customizable with a variety of outfit options to personalize your knight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic apex cloth physics for the character's clothing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a sword, banner, halberd, and shield.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="zombie_priest"&gt;&lt;a id="zombie_priest"&gt;Zombie - Priest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b3dfbfd3eeed148bbbbd2594f8715444b5221714.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c701da1e413d5ba8954bf5f16695a7b4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/04a16d0e-4995-4eed-aab2-d1ec1e23f44e"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.1 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introduce a dose of sacrilegious horror with the Zombie Priest. A symbol of corrupted faith, his tattered clerical garments and unsettling appearance create a truly memorable and disturbing foe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged to Epic skeleton for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game Ready &amp;amp; Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Textures &amp;amp; Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;IK Bones Included&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="fantasyhero"&gt;&lt;a id="fantasyhero" href="https://youtu.be/nfIAdU8cgHo"&gt;Fantasy Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/33ad6925ce1c5209e33726e68c592a19b2d80de3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=aef2d43059af4a7b8cbc1e46eb5b276f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/7e73566b-eb22-461d-a265-366b9e095939"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;4.18 – 4.27 and 5.0 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From the dense forests of Elderwood, introduce Ardan, the Forest Guardian, to your RPG. A formidable warrior and keeper of the sacred grove, this hero combines graceful combat with the magic of nature.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully modular with skin and outfit colour customization options to personalize your Hero&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic apex cloth physics&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Character comes equipped with a silver spear.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully compatible with Epic Skeletons for seamless integration and animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality textures and game ready models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="medievalprops_vol5_torchesandbraziers"&gt;&lt;a id="medievalprops_vol5_torchesandbraziers"&gt;Medieval Props Vol. 5 - Torches &amp; Braziers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/25078bf7d003175d8938c93ec25536a8be1444a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c9675eb5ae56295a42334f358a4ac190"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/94864536-bd34-4729-8abc-92dd18f60144"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Supports UE &lt;/em&gt;5.4 – 5.6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Illuminate your medieval worlds with this essential lighting pack. Ideal for adding warmth and atmosphere to dungeons, castles, and campsites.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1 Fire brazier, complete with a bed of coals.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2 Standing torches, large and small torch models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Customization options with versatile materials and instances to allow for quick changes to color and texture.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
