inations of instruments, great to use while making beats. That's not all! Inside, you will also find 20 MIDI files of all melodic elements, so you can create your own sounds in no-time. And the last part is the one-shots: drum samples, bass shots, instrumental and fx shots - polished and ready to feed your sampler. That's it, for today. Hope that will be enough to level up your music :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="melodicchilltrap_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="melodicchilltrap_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/kOw1cfcLIM8"&gt;Melodic Chill Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ea37ebffc8dcbde4b9f07e7f8b063d733757c36f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8bf1a095cfb680cecd5806aa8f57296d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;New collection, loaded with chilled Trap rhythms and spaced out melodies, ready to take you on a trip to a world of dreams... Drums &amp;amp; Percussion, Basslines, Pads, Keys, Guitars, Synths, Fx &amp;amp; Textures = you will find everything needed to produce Chill Trap in the highest level.  All content 100% royalty free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psytranceshamans_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="psytranceshamans_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/1yT0ValtKgs"&gt;Psytrance Shamans&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a2759a43a5a60145a9fcc4a163994634660e14ec.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=baaf56ebb0d3d46f95ee29029bc6c7d5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;New set of psychedelic sounds in this fresh Psytrance collection, coming from SHARP. The whole content was inspired by the top names and trending, progressive psy sound of today. Big pack of over 200 files, including Stems, One Shot Sample and MIDI files. Grouped into 5 key-labelled kits to make your workflow easy. You will find Basslines, Cinematic Drums, Kicks, Percussion &amp;amp; Fills, Plucks, Leads, Arps, Atmospheres, Effects, Vocals, Zaps and instruments such as Sitar, String, Dulcimer, Erhu, Flute, Arabian Guitar etc. "Psytrance Shamans" offers a wide range of royalty-free tools for producers seeking inspiration, while working on their next Psytrance release. This product will deliver the missing stuff, guaranteed!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapdinspace_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="trapdinspace_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/SP_UCbgrQtA"&gt;Trap'd in Space&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/588658097dc6c198357e80de875888be38a67200.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1a25aa4eca43e0b1570cfb4e44dc0326"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Spaced out melodies, twisted pianos, tight beats and interesting sounds, all mixed with lofi elements, making this new collection extremely useful. These type of sounds used in some of the biggest releases, will help you to stay on top of the game! Following the latest trends of trap music, this sample pack delivers 6 kits, packed with Drum Loops, Melodic Loops, MIDI files, Stems and One-Shot samples, all polished and ready to rumble in your sampler. Inspired by Gunna, Lil Baby, Metro Boomin and alike.  Let's take a trip to outer space and see what's there? You should :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="drillmoney_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="drillmoney_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/EPbNXCIlz2E"&gt;Drill Money&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9e5b41a736ccf53f413763dd5a593767424005d1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e14d692a118d8bf5755a7013c9674e09"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drill Money' from Function Loops takes us to New York, the hot spot of extremely popular Drill sound. Inspired by Pop Smoke, Fivio Foreign and names alike. This new pack is loaded with everything you need to produce fire beats: Drum Loops, Basslines, Melodic Loops, Keys, Synths, Strings and all the rest you hear in the demo. On top of the Loops, we also added a killer collection of One Shot samples, such as Kicks, Snares, Hats, Percussion - all polished and ready to rumble in your Sampler. As well, all melodic parts got a corresponding MIDI files, so you can re-create the sounds in no-time. All content 100% royalty-free. Now it's time to make some $$$!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psytrancealchemy_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="psytrancealchemy_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/14boU2QXllc"&gt;Psytrance Alchemy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/08b6b9a926aba157b36e58bfb099dd9f0fde631a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c7e6249df6af06498278fb59c462b2ef"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The long awaited collection of commercial Psytrance sounds is here and it's fire! With over 600MB of drums, basslines, melodic loops, fx, buildups and MIDI files, you'll get all you need to produce this popular genre.  Psytrance Alchemy delivers 200 files of pure magic. Recorded using both analog and digital gear, the sound quality is the best you'll find, guaranteed. By using the included MIDI melodies (20) and the drum patterns, you can re-create the sounds and give them your own touch. This product was inspired by the dominating sound of commercial Psytrance, which takes the world by storm. 100% royalty-free. Magic potion, anyone? :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="melodicsynthwave_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="melodicsynthwave_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/lfDCs9bMoqs"&gt;Melodic Synthwave&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a4bc96491ed47035e69a8d1e6819ec4a0c24960f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3597421346cc7c0b02963e22a0261b24"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The retro sounds are taking over the globe right now and this new collection delivers all the stuff needed to inject those vibes into your productions! Melodic Synthwave offers a wide selection of drum loops &amp;amp; one-shot samples, basslines, melodic and synth loops, atmospheres, plus MIDI files for maximum flexibility. All content is key and BPM labelled for ease for use, 100% royalty free. No matter if you're into Synthwave or just looking to add some retro feeling in your next tracks, this collection will do the work!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techhousecreatures_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techhousecreatures_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/z6jvR6ldmSQ"&gt;Tech House Creatures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2d55a03d2744022fcef63f5f6b91cddb2bf05190.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5a3520c3a2c392c4d5a8895890bdc39e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tech House Creatures delivers a huge pack of popular sounds to help you produce top-notch Tech House tracks, faster than you can imagine. Loaded with over 300 files, including 172 loops and 136 one-shot samples. Drums, Basslines, Synths, Vocals and FX are all there, polished and ready to be dropped in your productions. Drums are coming as full, top and stripped versions, for maximum flexibility. All sounds were inspired by top names. Get the sound that labels are seeking today! The content is 100% royalty free, which means you can use our sounds in your commercial projects with no hidden costs. We are all Tech House Creatures...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="acidtechno2020_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="acidtechno2020_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/yik5pGtCp_4"&gt;Acid Techno 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cd1e9ae3e031823d76a6c0dc122e92e7f12fdb46.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a04d2b72d4b391f241f9e46b56fdd17a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Acid Techno 2020 from SHARP takes inspiration from the sets of Charlotte de Witte and Amelie Lens. It brings that powerful &amp;amp; crowd hypnotizing rhythm straight to your studio.  We have included drum loops, basslines, acid lines, pads and deep Techno vocals. On top of these, you will also find bass and synth one shots, SFX shots and drum hits, such as kicks, claps, hats and rides. All drum loops are delivered as full, stripped, kick only and top versions. A big pack for the price, over 300 sounds! Of course, all content is 100% royalty free. All content is labelled with key and BPM information (130 BPM). Killer collection of pure dance floor energy!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="collinwatt_futureblueshop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="collinwatt_futureblueshop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/8sDKbmR2lec"&gt;Collin Watt - Future Blues Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/28b6c72d974037b281563d8d04ea1ae1cfcaf682.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f0c56e853c142c8bb2e2ef6ab68b97d5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collin Watt is a composer and producer based out of Los Angeles, CA. With 12 years of guitar and bass playing under his belt, he has developed his own style. Collin Watt uses elements such as blues, jazz, pop, and hip hop to blend what he calls 'future blues hop'. Inside this pack you'll find many of his own composition and productions filled with creative processing and smooth licks.  This is like no other guitar pack you will find... On top of the guitars, there's also a comprehensive collection of original vocal acapellas, drums, synth loops and one shot samples. All content recorded at 24-bit best quality and is 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="livepopguitars_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="livepopguitars_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/JgKtswURei0"&gt;Live Pop Guitars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e837a94f5be5a283e95c24f719dfeda11ae2a280.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c0af554c14a747ac98d68a9abb508a9d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Guitars are often the weak point in music production. Either they're not convincing, because they were made with virtual instruments, or they just simply don't have that wow factor that keeps the listener connected. We feel it's a missing piece in the market...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;That's why we created "Live Pop Guitars", a pack that contains only guitars, recorded with a professional guitarist. Inside you will find most current sounds, such as those found in pop &amp;amp; dance hits with millions of views on Youtube.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Pop Guitars" is versatile in that it comes with guitar loops in both dry or wet versions, also with a detailed folder of single guitar shots. Which you can easily load into any sampler and create the desired rhythms. As for the loops, you will find a lot of rhythms, riffs, melodies and hooks - ready to refresh any project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In detail, "Pop Guitars" has 60 dry loops, 60 wet loops, and 60 one-shot guitar samples. All the loops and shots are professionally labeled with key and BPM information (where applicable).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Of course, all sounds are 100% royalty-free. That means, you pay for the pack once and get a license to use it in all your projects, without thinking about additional costs. And we guarantee you will use it often, because ""Live Pop Guitars"" is the product, that will solve your guitar problems, without paying a fortune for pro-guitar player!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techxafro_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techxafro_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/b9pR3_lNCNc"&gt;Tech x Afro&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aae98fb30b233a4752832fb71c1ee257b721b5b3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d6b65bb2dd13a4becec07c2a38f45c3e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Afro rhythms are everywhere, taking over many genres in the music industry and gaining huge popularity. Especially it blends fantastic with Tech House, that's why we present you "Tech X Afro" - a brand new sample pack featuring this cool combo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Tech X Afro" brings some of the best sounding grooves, similar to those you hear in big records. There's a perfect balance between quality and quantity. Absolutely no filler sounds here - we picked only the best loops and samples created by our talented producer. But even so, it resulted in a fat collection of over 320 files!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boost your creativity with the included Afro Percussion Loops, Techy Drum Loops, Basslines, Textures, Synths, Vocal Chops, and FX Loops. On top of Loops, we added a nice collection of 95 One-Shot Samples, including Kicks, Claps, Sub Hits, Percussion &amp;amp; Hats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In terms of technical details, "Tech X Afro" is as follows: 488MB in size (unzipped), 328 loops &amp;amp; one-shots, 24-bit WAV files. Of course, all samples are 100% royalty-free, as usual.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="soulwave_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="soulwave_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/kwA2j8gLRqo"&gt;Soulwave&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c5c10c5a691e3610c401d50cc6db5173a0a94fa3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7ee929cb6912816b524ef3109cc05257"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are proud to introduce 'Soulwave' - a forward-thinking pack, loaded with intelligent sounds for producers seeking to produce soulful and elegant music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It has 380MB of Drums, Basslines, Arps, Pads, Keys, Vocal Chops, Effects, Synths, Plucks, Music Loops and all the other stuff you can hear in the demo. All the sounds are included, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Took us some time to craft this collection, every sound was processed with care, as always. You are getting a premium sample pack, that will inspire you in the studio, guaranteed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nightstream_lo-fihiphop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="nightstream_lo-fihiphop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/dMRY3_zrrXI"&gt;Night Stream: Lo-fi Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/05b7aadc6aec45bafe5ebf9a2f754bea98be6498.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ea2ba7eedbbb7f75321e8627b1612c6d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Night Stream: Lo-Fi Hip Hop' from Function Loops is a comprehensive collection of lo-fi and chilled sounds, made for that 'midnight coffee' vibes!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Music to study/relax to' is taking over Youtube and streams worldwide, which proves this genre is what you wanna do.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our new sample pack delivers all the goods: Atmospheres, Bass Loops, Drums and Cymbals, Guitar Loops, Melodic Loops, SFX and One Shots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also included Bass and Melodies as MIDI files, so you can work out your magic in no-time. All our content is 100% royalty free, as usual.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Let's roll!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="viraltrap_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="viraltrap_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/64NNwOUtex4"&gt;Viral Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2bd3052c9caffa0039448c7fc50474ee28130b6c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e07835c5fc3c7beac9257cbdc6e7ae6f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Viral Trap' from Function Loops delivers five new construction kits, inspired by current top hits.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We checked what's trending right now, to bring this fresh set of viral sounds, to help you reach the next level in your productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each kit comes with Loops, One Shots, Stems, MIDI files. Expect cutting-edge 808s, Drums, Percussion, Basslines, Melodies and FX sounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content 100% royalty-free. Use our sounds in your commercial projects, sell to labels, stream, perform - no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to go viral?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techhousexrave_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techhousexrave_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/Bkq4C64ZZLo"&gt;Tech House x Rave&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1f983ac5b156f4345610970ecaa90bea58d76c9c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ee2f264c1179c0cc64dcf7394933a887"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tech House music is evolving all the time into new directions and one of the most popular right now is the combination with old-school and Rave sounds. This new and fresh collection from SHARP delivers exactly that! No shortcuts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As always, we are trying our best to deliver unique stuff to work with. This time, we took inspiration from the most popular tech house releases and mixed them with amen breaks, old school organs and synths, crazy rave fx and chopped vocals = what else do you need?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We came up with quite a big pack of over 300 files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In detail you'll find: 5 breakbeat drum loops, 10 bass loops, 70 drum loops, 15 fx loops, 6 snare fill loops, 25 synth loops, 16 vocal loops and 120 one-shots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;35 MIDI files included too, for maximum flexibility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don't miss this cool trend, happening right now! Drop these sounds in your next productions, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="malepopvocals_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="malepopvocals_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/KssXH6845Gk"&gt;Male Pop Vocals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/67bc5d10fd2f5a1e21182efc7955014422a0f0c3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81c367247a9437d0492bcd1c85d7d7f1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;We feel, there's a serious lack of male vocals for Pop, Future Rnb, Melodic Trap, Future Bass and commercial genres alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;That's why we deliver this new collection, loaded with 500MB of Male Vocal Loops, Drums, Basslines, Instrumental Loops, Music Loops and all the rest you hear in the demo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vocals come as dry and wet versions, full acapellas and separated vocal loops, for maximum flexibility. Vocal content is original, recorded at top quality, 100% royalty-free. You will also find some cool vocal chops!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On top of loops, we included MIDI files for all instrumentals, so you can create your melodies in no-time. You are also getting a comprehensive collection of One Shot Samples, including Drum Shots and Instrument Shots. You can load these into a sampler and have some fun!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In total, this amazing pack is loaded with over 500MB of content, 186 files, 24-bit WAV format.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="drillmusic_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="drillmusic_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/UyhhsNbCYlI"&gt;Drill Music&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/72e2a7a5d8bd3706597171c595d9b6c07f5a7c16.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9656483b85c5083f061bef06beb24bc4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coming directly from New York city, this new collection from SHARP will blow your mind. If you're a fan of Drill or planning to transform yourself into this extremely popular genre, then cut the talking and listen the demo!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Drill Music' offers most innovative sounds in Drill scene. Our producer lives and breathes this style, so we know what we're doing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find 150 sounds, including Loops, Stems, One Shots and MIDI files, for maximum flexibility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is original and 100% royalty free. Use these sounds in your own music, sell to labels and lease to singers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now it's time to Drill!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lazylo-fiandchilltrap_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="lazylo-fiandchilltrap_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/3mJrjQnsf4A"&gt;Lazy Lo-fi &amp; Chill Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/39493ebc4a89a5f77468ed41ab2160f6c5e270fb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=485dd65600e9fc054f592ac130566c3b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Lazy Lofi &amp;amp; Chill Trap" brings unique collection for producers seeking to inject interesting lofi and chilled sounds into their productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with Drums &amp;amp; Percussion, Bass Loops, Instruments and melodies, Music Loops, Vocal Chops and One Shot Samples.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To make this collection innovative, we recorded some Foley sounds in our studio and at home to capture all kind of live sounds and transform them into percussion, you won't hear anywhere else!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds original and 100% royalty-free. Now, let's relax and dive into the chill...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="slaphouse_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="slaphouse_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/N7rvarsO4_4"&gt;Slap House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cbfa7acc961455dfc1227c6ceed5de11289fa856.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a16877a11573cbc015b799d244ee81ca"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;One of the genres in the spotlight right now is the sound inspired by Alok, Bhaskar, Dynoro and alike. They are on top of the game!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our new collection delivers all the goods you need to tap into this market. 475MB of Drum Loops, Basslines, Synth Loops, FX Loops, MIDI files and One Shot Samples. All content 100% royalty-free, use in your commercial projects, no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also decided to add 25 bonus Vocal loops from our best selling The New EDM pack, to spice things up! We are always on the look for fresh ideas, we think this new pack will help you a lot.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="darkandacidtechno_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="darkandacidtechno_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/_6k2N6uxcBw"&gt;Dark &amp; Acid Techno&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/721b21a77d01948f9e91f08a456043a06f4cef48.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=63a401ea6434814caaf3f5738c9c9c2e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Freshly squeezed acid rhythms and dark grooves, coming at you from SHARP lab.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;299 production tools for serious Techno producers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drum Loops, Basslines, Pads , Rides , Synth Loops and extra collection of One Shots, including Bass, Drums, FX and Synth Shots, ready to be dropped into the sampler to build original sounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As all our previous sample packs, the content is 100 % original and 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are coming in 24-bit WAV quality, inspired by top labels and artists around the globe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now it's time to go underground...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="samuraihiphop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="samuraihiphop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/xBI2jckAzzU"&gt;Samurai Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e75f0b54c57549fb79637fb8fc7cdbb98e4b5517.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e6dfb3a3baff9a7cb42e4204f42e2204"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's Samurai sh*t! Dark &amp;amp; mysterious melodies, deep 808's, super tight drums and innovative percussion, weird SFX - this is all you get in our 'Samurai Hip Hop' collection, coming from SHARP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Over 200 files, delivered as Loops and One Shot Samples, ready to rock your lovely sampler. All content you hear in the demo is included, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All samples processed with best gear, recorded at 24-bit quality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get these interesting sounds into your next tracks right now!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are coming in 24-bit WAV quality, inspired by top labels and artists around the globe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now it's time to go underground...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lo-fihiphopandlivesounds_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="lo-fihiphopandlivesounds_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/3gvb8pUtty8"&gt;Lo-fi Hip Hop &amp; Live Sounds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b38dea2bbc33e1930ba09a79ba357409043303bf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3fc1ec8e38eb9c3c9a95b636a2741446"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A refreshing collection of lo-fi beats with emotional pianos, soulful saxophone and guitars!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Loaded with bunch of inspiration, including Hip Hop Drums, Fills, Basslines, Live Keys, Sax Loops, Guitars, Music Loops, FX and super useful One Shot Samples. Most of the stuff delivered as Dry &amp;amp; Wet versions, where applicable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This new collection will be a pleasure to sample into all Hip Hop sub-genres, as well as Soul, Trap, RnB and many other type of beats, where live touch is needed. 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techhousemagic_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techhousemagic_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/rqLq-z08DCI"&gt;Tech House Magic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/efc55c6669c7e897473bbd85f7695494a3ca5ac0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7bf179353c7bc08438f6fda0a39da7f8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Long time in the making, finally we are back with another supreme collection of Tech House, that will blow your mind!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Filled with bunch of unique, weird and special sounds - this new pack from SHARP is going to do magic with your productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A big sample pack, loaded with 282 files, including absolutely all the tools needed for modern Tech House producer. You will find Basslines, Drum Loops, Synth Loops, Fills, FX and Vocals plus comprehensive collection of One Shot Samples, including Bass Shots, Kicks, Claps &amp;amp; Percussion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are getting 152 Loops, 85 One Shots and 45 MIDI files, for maximum flexibilily. In our professional opinion, this is one of the best releases from SHARP to-date.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Check the demo and you will feel the magic!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="lo-fihiphopandfuturesoul_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="lo-fihiphopandfuturesoul_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/FhLElVMhv8E"&gt;Lo-fi Hip Hop &amp; Future Soul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e9f6c9f16db6c6843ec5160037e043f104441116.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=daa3da9ba63a504a9127b0c5c6fa2ae0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Over 600MB of versatile content in this new and amazing collection of lo-fi sounds. Live guitars, Foley sounds, drums, basslines, melodies &amp;amp; instruments, pianos, FX vinyl and tape sounds, unique atmospheres and everything else you can imagine!  'Lofi Hiphop &amp;amp; Future Soul' delivers a comprehensive collection for Lo-fi producers, including: Loops, One Shots and a super useful collection of 50 Serum Presets, to help you design interesting and new sound in no-time. Fresh content, originally recorded and processed by our talented producers. 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="memphishiphop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="memphishiphop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/91900tfSHf0"&gt;Memphis Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2c486243304dc035ce4f6bf26a338a993e57219d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=105ab5257561bbc33c5015c092e1dfec"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Memphis!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Being inspired by the 90's Memphis hip hop scene, this new collection delivers dark vibes, lo-fi synths and old school beats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Memphis Hip-Hop proudly brings 5 full construction kits, including loops, one-shot samples, MIDI files and stems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As usual, all content is 100% royalty-free. This means you can use our sounds in your commercial projects, with no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapheroes_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="trapheroes_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/5Juu9bEK_Ak"&gt;Trap Heroes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/484d0806c41dd671689a86a353549e91c4727054.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7e54c19fa4234bab8a8222b4515ae5b1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new collection of kits inspired by your favorite Trap heroes. Including 5 construction kits and a fat folder of bonus files for maximum pleasure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each kit is coming with Loops, Shots, Stems and MIDI files. You’re getting absolutely everything needed to produce ‘that sound’.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drums, 808’s, Stabs, Glitched Arps, Melodies, Effects and everything else you can hear in the demo, are included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On top of 5 new kits, you will find bonus folder of extra 3 kits, collected from previous popular packs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty-free, use in your own productions, sell to labels, stream on radios, perform and collect all income to yourself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="heavybass_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="heavybass_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/45Pl7x57cX8"&gt;Heavy Bass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9ca0c9304b8dba6d76fba36db3572c72bffb07ca.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b8d27460209b8e06c0c3e6b2c15f82d5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Crazy collection of super heavy sounds to help you produce Dubstep, Midtempo, Riddim and other heavy bass music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with Construction Kits, Stems, Loops, Samples, MIDI files and bunch of kick ass Serum Presets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fat collection of 240+ files, over 1GB of stuff. All 100% royalty free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="90shiphopstash_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="90shiphopstash_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/m1HB6kS_zw0"&gt;90's Hip Hop Stash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f7df483fa8af4340aa8ce0b717740d982f53adcd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=42241ac4c84ef04c06d93882a7b3054c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Back to the 90's in style!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this special new hood-flava episode, we bring you a hot collection of 90's-style, crackly vinyl beats and treats to make your studio-time more inspiring.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Juicy hooks, Medikal pianos, 808 basslines and spliffy beats, all perfectly tweaked and ready for action.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapordown_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="trapordown_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/szcYa9V963I"&gt;Trap or Down&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c8125372e2dd3add77eef07271e089357d46aef4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=94fba278fcd13e5338f5a74f172ad5f4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Trap or Drown' from Function Loops delivers five fresh construction kits, loaded with Stems, Loops, Shots and MIDI files. Sounds built around sinister piano melodies, hard hitting beats, pumping 808s and dark, vintage vibes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty free, you can use the sounds in your commercial releases and collect all income to yourself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trap or drown!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techhousearcade_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techhousearcade_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/OHdQn3T7iwo"&gt;Tech House Arcade&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/429cf916cf91e6d619745137b551d0c5ac391d35.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5d94f397faf5848bb3d7b59fadf2eda5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;New collection of sweaty Tech House sounds, including Drums, Basslines, Synths, FX , Vocal Loops, One Shots and MIDI files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collection inspired by top artists and labels of the scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Those teeth breaking grooves, insanely tight drums, fat rolling basslines, deep synths and vocals = all there.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to start playing? Welcome to Tech House Arcade!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cloudtrapandemohiphop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="cloudtrapandemohiphop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/rObVqPm-eFg"&gt;Cloud Trap &amp; Emo Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e7546f9f7f04e9ff4595524fb78b328fb9c8fcaa.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=891c91989f947dc5bbc0d28335365c3a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new collection of hazy sounds, inspired by extremely popular Emo Rappers. The sound taking over the world by storm, now at your studio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Five construction kits, loaded with deep beats &amp;amp; basslines, ethereal vocals, emo melodies &amp;amp; lofi sounds, spaced out FX and all the rest needed to produce this contemporary Hip Hop genre.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All vocal were recorded in our studios, then processed into chopped vocal loops. Each kit comes with Stems, Loops, Shots, MIDI &amp;amp; Presets - full production toolkit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="majorlatintrapandpop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="majorlatintrapandpop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/VQmU4SgqDE8"&gt;Major Latin Trap &amp; Pop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/349d2d49e880d414a2b25adcb728722552622887.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d46d9ff5b5b8ec1b4afb301008ae0607"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Major Latin Trap &amp;amp; Pop' is a new sample pack inspired by Bad Bunny, J Balvin, Farruko, Ozuna and similar names, dominating the charts around the globe today.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With music trends changing, Latino urban artists are gearing to the genre, and for them, Latin Trap is changing the game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Blend of Trap beats, Reggaeton vibes &amp;amp; future Pop sounds, this collection is guaranteed to inspire and help you take your music to the next level. On top of all , every kit is loaded with quality Vocal Acapellas, to spice it all.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Innovation is key and this fresh sample pack is nothing you gonna find on the sample market, guaranteed. It's the new expansion that the urban genre needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hiphopwaves_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="hiphopwaves_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/d-zt1Ext3_o"&gt;Hip Hop Waves&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a191f9978bef117b4358bc4aac7c507461b9034f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=80d2952a85496936136effc96220ae60"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fresh set of Hip Hop Waves, collection inspired by main sound of the year. Delivering five Construction Kits loaded with Loops, Stems, Shots and MIDI files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You get bunch of inspiring sounds, no matter if you're the producer or the rapper. All kits comes with full mixdowns, so you can lay the vox on.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are 100% royalty-free, means you can use them in your commercial projects, no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now it's time to make some waves in the scene!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="majorhiphopandvocalrnb_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="majorhiphopandvocalrnb_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/mKUztGpMpBg"&gt;Major Hip Hop &amp; Vocal RnB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6c8f2c9cd941ba3f83cd68c6d48cb63db1d26f29.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c694bff3d9188fb0a7876b83ddf43a76"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This new collection of perfectly crafted samples, is probably our best release till now.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inspired by Drake, Ariana Grande and big names alike, it's a complete solution for producers seeking to make hit records.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It has all the most current sounds and production tools, including drums, percussion, basslines, 808s, pads, guitars, keys, synths, sfx and gorgeous female acapellas, in dry and wet versions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All 100% royalty-free, means you can use the sounds in your music, release on labels, sell to singers and make money off your music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Just listen the demo and you will understand what we're talking about, the pack is fire :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psytranceandprogressive_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="psytranceandprogressive_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/6KlLyY93PkM"&gt;Psytrance &amp; Progressive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6dc1f036df19880691a3a9512e4ad0b25d4d47d8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1be56d98c9da96f3b45c109c7582aec6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new collection of Progressive Psytrance sounds, including five Construction Kits loaded with the most advanced and innovative production tools, reflecting the sound you'll hear in the summer festivals this year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll better get ready!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each kit comes with Full Stems, Loops, One Shots and MIDI files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We would like to underline and explain about Full Stems:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These are complete exports of the construction kits. They are exported from zero till the end, as you get a remix stems, for example. We tried to bounce as many parts into these stems, but some of them still have silence in the beginning, so you know exactly which musical part comes where in the track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;How to use stems? Simply import all of them together in your DAW, so you will have an arrangement of around 1 minute, you can take it from there and get inspired quickly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don't need Stems? There are corresponding Loops included as well, these are short versions of the stems. That's why they sound the same, but useful in a different way.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One Shots &amp;amp; MIDI files included, too.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hope that make sense :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nu-discoandfunk_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="nu-discoandfunk_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/jxhdn-KpVaI"&gt;Nu-Disco &amp; Funk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4eae083624ce68461d2a81363e9f227b4faa8a68.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=570dafa7489aa8bd9c8126dfe69b6ebd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Nu-Disco &amp;amp; Funk with Live Guitars' is something different, than usual Function Loops release. It's a collection of rare grooves, you won't find much on the market today.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Four construction kits, coming along 88 funky guitar loops, played and recorded live to deliver that authentic feel. Everything is key and bpm labelled, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This product will save your time for searching and booking a producer and guitar player, to record, edit and produce the sounds. As well, will save you bunch of money!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to inject disco and funk vibes into your project, this pack will make your day.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="universalpop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="universalpop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/QOsuZKsRZCs"&gt;Universal Pop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1f8003d9d493218871bad4b0e3c0e3d0d8f384ad.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=892da10dc74c4cfebc6a4309c93663a6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Brand new collection of Pop sounds, inspired by the most influential player in the industry - universal music and their fine roster of artists.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack is loaded with most advanced production tools needed to produce commercial music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with 5 brand new construction kits, plus a bonus, 2 extra kits, making this collection a huge, 7 kit pack. A whopping 1.7GB unzipped, over 290 files in total!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All kits loaded with stems, loops, shots, midi and gorgeous vocal acapellas.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to produce music that labels are seeking today, then you're in the right place!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;File types included:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Loops: 4 to 8 bar audio files, 24-Bit WAV. Simply drag and drop them into your DAW and manipulate to fit your project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One-Shots: Single shot samples. Good to use in your favorite sampler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full Stems: These are long, arranged files. Simply import them into any DAW and you will get an already arranged piece, ready for further development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;MIDI: Melodic parts also come as MIDI files, giving you maximum flexibility to tweak, recreate and make your own sounds, using VSTis or samplers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futuresoulandmelodictrap_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futuresoulandmelodictrap_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/0WwX_m6DBJM"&gt;Future Soul &amp; Melodic Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2756243d69187f5cc3aec7a1a28fdb8bd262ae43.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d29edff0a1025ab073d6f1ca2248a35f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new sample pack, loaded with soulful sounds infused with forward thinking electronic production.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elements of Electronica, Rnb, Trap &amp;amp; Soul, delivering the ultimate collection to help you produce this popular genre.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5 Construction Kits, Loops, MIDI files and One-shots = all you need is inside.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every kit comes with drums, percussion, basslines, 808s, chords, arps, pianos, keys, vocal chops, live instruments, FX loops and all the rest you hear in the demos, plus much more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% royalty free, as all our sounds and products.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="primecuts_riddimdubstep_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="primecuts_riddimdubstep_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/4lmlXdLjQNs"&gt;Prime Cuts - Riddim Dubstep&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3eff21c3a89e9c2585a918cccf97744453543a19.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d0e24fec2b542a6981ca337af99afa2a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find some of the hardest and dirtiest sounds in this new collection by Function Loops!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We deliver you the Prime Cuts of Dubstep &amp;amp; Riddim, packed in 5 key-labelled Construction Kits. Expect nasty Drum Loops &amp;amp; One Shots, Synth and Bass Loops, SFX Loops &amp;amp; MIDI files (where applicable).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Let's get dirty?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="90sinfusedhiphop_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="90sinfusedhiphop_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/K9P0t6QVTOE"&gt;90's Infused Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a42228e4003465a89416849cf0a3a21042e50592.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1179ef94dd1cd1e0377884bcaae2d6bd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;'90's Infused Hip Hop' from Function Loops delivers over 300MB of modern Hip Hop sounds, infused with live instruments and old school vibes, making this pack super interesting and unique.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with Drum Loops, Melodic Loops, Music Loops, One Shots and MIDI files, everything 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find Beats, Basslines, Guitars, Pianos, Sax, Synths and Vocals - perfect stash for any Hip Hop producer. One Shots including Bass, Kicks, Snares, Hats and Instruments - all ready for you favorite samplers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grab this toolbox now and start crafting your next Hip Hop production!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sacredpsytrance_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="sacredpsytrance_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/7-BtwhfHbNQ"&gt;Sacred Psytrance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/57b736ed24562eacb634cdd13742c8958f96e27a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=adaee12abfb0c3aa77d4cc34b444149d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's time to give some real Psytrance sounds for real Psytrance producers!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Incredible quality, psychedelic content - this is what the new collection is all about...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Just listen the demo to get the idea of what's packed inside ""Sacred Psytrance"".&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A professional producer toolkit, loaded with over 280+ sounds, including 238 loops and 46 one-shot samples. Over 1GB of loops and one-shots!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The main focus of this product is the Synth Loops. All of them carefully produced, using both analog and digital equipment. Also, Bass one-shots will be super useful for your favorite sampler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On top of that, you'll find some kicks, bass loops, percussion, fx and all the rest you hear in the demo preview.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In detail, you are getting 177 Synth Loops, 10 Bass Loops, 26 Drum Loops, 9 Percussion Loops, 16 FX Loops, 42 Bass Shots and 4 Kick Shots. Everything key &amp;amp; BPM labelled, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These sounds are sacred, use them wisely.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapscale_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="trapscale_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/Ucdbrm6_Y7o"&gt;Trap Scale&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/299dd02b41ada6b3aedffc0f41ba7a5520e66778.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81b1dec5ef69e0961e1af1e3ed313614"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Trap Scale' from Function Loops is a brand new production toolkit for Trap &amp;amp; Hiphop producers, seeking to inject popular sounds into their next productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This time the focus is on darker, melodic vibes. Total of over 380MB of stuff, including five royalty-free construction kits.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find Stems, Drum &amp;amp; Melodic Loops, MIDI files and One Shots, ready for your favorite sampler. 808s, kicks, snares, percussion, keys, pianos, flutes, plucks, vocal chants and all the rest is packed inside.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boom!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="flawlesstechno_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="flawlesstechno_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/lhj8PrVdb74"&gt;Flawless Techno&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2635b4a08c982ece8341727bebaa7f11061df693.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8f482387f12765e9bc0a502425f29b25"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Flawless Techno from SHARP offers a wide variety of production tools, including over 290 files. Perfectly crafted and ready to be dropped instantly into your next tracks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A full producer pack, loaded with bunch of inspiration and every sound you can hear in the demo is included. All content is 100% royalty-free, use our sounds in your music, sell to labels, perform and gain success!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In detail, you are getting: 20 Bass Loops, 99 Drum Loops, 14 Pads, 22 Synth Loops, 20 Ride Loops, 20 Bass Shots, 82 Drum Shots and 20 Synth Shots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This new collection is here to help you get flawless techno tracks in no-time!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="groovetechhouse_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="groovetechhouse_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/GT01HXGomNE"&gt;Groove Tech House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1812024c4502ebd7ad3fa60537a3bcf9a2b9ed4b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=53185970115050130aa86e1a8ff2b255"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A fresh collection for all Tech House producers, seeking inspiration and fasten studio workflow. Bunch of groovy rhythms inside this new release!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A professional pack, loaded with Bass Loops, Bass Shots, Drums Loops, Drum Shots, SFX Loops, Fills, Synth Loops and Vocal Loops.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All the studio tools are inside. 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inspired by top 10 tech house charts and sounds, that labels are seeking today!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dubstepandriddim2020_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="dubstepandriddim2020_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/djIzgs6RrJY"&gt;Dubstep &amp; Riddim 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d3f145b2d697a1377657bb3676b83ab52c278a8a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=95be0a4409cc27b66dd3ce228c1d90d6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new killer collection of epic sounds has arrived!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our producers are back from 2020 to deliver some of the nastiest, hard hitting sounds for Dubstep &amp;amp; Riddim.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You're getting Construction Kits, Loops &amp;amp; Samples, bunch of Drums, Basslines, Synths, FX and other useful dirt.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maybe the world will end in 2020? Probably not :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="melodictrapandrnb_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="melodictrapandrnb_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/eugcYMWGzws"&gt;Melodic Trap &amp; RnB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3703cfc5eddc9fcb49e12984fd7a93e8640a8dcb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cc7e25082e03dc5b20982c2106f03abb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Melodic Trap &amp;amp; RnB' from Function Loops is super innovative collection with future vision in mind. Extremely interesting percussion loops, vocal chops, synths, basslines, music loops, fx and everything else a modern producer needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All formats included, for maximum flexibility: Loops, One Shots and MIDI files. Over 490MB of content. 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Blend of Trap, Hip Hop, Future RnB, Chillout with melodic vibes, these sounds will stand out in your productions. If you are looking for futuristic and fresh concept , then this pack is for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="techhousefunk_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="techhousefunk_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/_gVZTNgDj3I"&gt;Tech House Funk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ae8dc50f54c0cb0afb281dd2ed00fd226206384d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d912700bd1c774cab7e41ae86a0f7830"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A 250MB of futuristic and super funky Tech House sounds for that 'unique' vibe!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This collection from SHARP is a little different. Loaded with funky and crazy sounds to spice your productions and make them stand out.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with full arsenal, including Basslines, Drum Loops, FX Loops, Synths, Vocals, MIDI files and One Shots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty free, means you can grab these killer sounds, drop them into your next tracks, sell to labels and collect all the income to yourself!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inspired by some of the biggest productions around the world today, the new and interesting trend taking over the charts. Now, you can inject these sounds into your productions in the blink of an eye!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's time for Tech House Funk!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="houseroom_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="houseroom_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/O1f9j5ueNZ0"&gt;House Room&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4f9cec06eacdd036b1f23d502bb3deba80782e13.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2b8a4b6c6621e3aa7030605e5007213e