der, loaded with String &amp;amp; Percussion rhythms for the extra touch.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collection full of amazing melodies and cinematic themes, to fuel any kind of production. Add an interesting intro or use powerful drums in a break, just before the drop. Your fans will love it!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futurebassworldwide_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futurebassworldwide_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/wtJhoorQDgw"&gt;Future Bass Worldwide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bc942104aecbb63cd8859514ba91aab5f46d004e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bc2050bf729f05685f9667ad61b1f255"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new set of melodic Future Bass sounds, guaranteed to inspire you in the upcoming studio sessions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full arsenal of sonic tools: Beats, Basslines, Melodies, Vocals and everything else needed to help you produce class-A tracks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are 100% royalty-free, use them in your music, sell to labels, release, perform – no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grab this pack and start building your next Future Bass banger!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="progressivepsytranceempire_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="progressivepsytranceempire_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/lriOCxW_vz4"&gt;Progressive Psytrance Empire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6f139466cf1553c2ffb0239f6011ae6a89f0c9d8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c1c2a1fdfd92075ee93407c67c676477"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;‘Progressive Psytrance Empire’ brings 6 key-labelled, huge sounding kits, loaded with Stems, Loops, Single Shots &amp;amp; MIDI files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As always, inspired by the biggest labels and popular sound, which makes impact in the scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re giving you the right tools, to help you succeed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kits come with Full Stems, just import to the DAW and you will have the arrangements, as you hear in the demos - perfect to get some inspiration and start your tracks quick.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Kits are also loaded with industry-standard Loops, One Shots &amp;amp; MIDI files, for maximum flexibility. This is a big pack, including 292 Files, 2.3GB of content, 100% Royalty-Free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get this collection now and start building your own empire! Inspiration guaranteed...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futuresoul_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futuresoul_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/ZyZTnJbxMsM"&gt;Future Soul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0a3bcf2ebdcee5ab01cb31bc9b17ecf345619f40.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a405ce5547c402617c26020f3e50520a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;‘Future Soul’ – amazing fusion of Trap, Future R’n’B and organic Electronica grooves with soulful melodies, deep vocal chops, crispy percussion and all the tools you need, to produce this outstanding genre.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;‘Future Soul’ delivers five key and BPM labelled construction kits, loaded with Loops, One-Shot samples and MIDI files, for maximum flexibility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You find Drums, Basslines, Arps, Keys, Plucks, Vocal Chops, Chords, Pads, Pianos and all the rest you can hear in the demo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is original and 100% royalty-free, outstanding quality product. Use our sounds in your music, sell to labels and collect all the royalties to yourself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grab ‘Future Soul’ now and start producing your next hit!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="wonkytrap_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="wonkytrap_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/DZKP71yuSXo"&gt;Wonky Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ca67d083a7567557a5854a0e69be040b4c301a64.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2c331a556842dcb5e547a10229e3aa64"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Wonky Trap from SHARP (Function Loops Label Group) delivers 5 killer construction kits, loaded with insane set of sounds, including blasting Beats, 808’s, Leads, Vox, FX and all the rest you can hear in the demo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All kits are key and BPM labelled, for ease use. Packed with Loops, One Shots and MIDI files. Over 350MB of content, 149 files in total. 100% royalty-free.  Pick this collection now to help you produce crazy riddims!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="darkscience_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="darkscience_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/8kTl3XUGoZU"&gt;Dark Science&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3890b6d654c08a0f78b105615c7017ca9dcd8028.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a168c2693d721f0b2f004747b3526839"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our sound scientists are proud to present "Dark Science" collection full of different vibes you knew till now.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are getting 6 key and bpm labelled construction kits, loaded with bunch of studio goodness: Kicks, Percussion, Basslines, Synths, Noizes, various FX and unique sounds to make your productions interesting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All kits come with Loops, Shots &amp;amp; MIDI for maximum flexibility. 24-bit WAV, 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We're all looking to stand out of the crowd with unique music, right? Inject these amazing sounds in your next tracks and you will.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futureg-house_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futureg-house_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/WXxIusphllw"&gt;Future G-House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/18a7a8ace96bda1d2f5f2f5e03102d28c4908bc5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f9741272f4fa3bcb5c92c94ac8edb2d6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Great collection of over 300 files for G-House productions. You will find 5 x Key labelled kits and a bunch of bonus content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All Kits charged with Loops, Shots, MIDI &amp;amp; Presets - maximum flexibility in the studio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sounds coming from a ghost producer, which is involved in G-House scene, so he knows what he's doing. All content 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find Drums, Leads, FX , Drops and everything else you hear in the demo. We also added additional folder loaded with G-House kicks and percussion elements. Let's rock!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="toosexyvocalsbytonka_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="toosexyvocalsbytonka_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/gfb90LXPjY8"&gt;Too Sexy Vocals by Tonka&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f77af15a15e060874586d22222cf7d0ea1cacb47.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4202953335070ea67fbfd9ba77e6cde6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;You asked for more Tonka, so we brought her back! This time in a gorgeously dubby installment of her sexy acapellas, Tonka has delivered her finest performance yet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inside this beautifully produced vocal pack, you'll find everything you need for your deep-styled productions, from smooth vocal phrases, to sexy whispering voices and cool house one shots, it's all there. As always, these phrases can be used as they are, or cut up and looped for that sought-after hypnotic effect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vocals will sit tight in any production looking for deep &amp;amp; sexy feeling. All content is Key and BPM labelled for ease of use. Vocals come as Dry/Wet versions for maximum flexibility. 100% royalty-free content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can hear Tonka's voice in almost every Deep House set today, we set a new standard. Grab these fresh vocals and sample them right away in your next productions, no matter which genre you are into.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bedroompopvocals_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="bedroompopvocals_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/-G-fo7m6j6M"&gt;Bedroom Pop Vocals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/58c9960a4fd2c5d05ef4dc827f20268f7feffb48.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ff46864102c0b4fe07b1af96c5fdc81b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Bedroom Pop Vocals" is an original sample pack featuring 4 full song construction kits designed to add a personal touch to your music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With instrument loops, mesmerizing vocals, dynamic drum loops, and versatile one shots, this collection ignites your creativity!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Capture intimate performances with soulful guitars, delicate pianos, evocative synths, and atmospheric textures and unique fx.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The vocals range from delicate to powerful hooks, infusing your tracks with genuine emotion. Dynamic drum loops and customizable one shots provide rhythmic foundations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;'Bedroom Pop Vocals' is ideal for adding heartfelt performances and emotional depth to any genre. Let your music speak from the heart and connect with your audience on a deeper level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the soul of your productions with our brand new vocals!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="soundsofamapiano_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="soundsofamapiano_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/pvYuQVDeMFQ"&gt;Sounds of Amapiano&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fcc438daaf70387374ea1b69ab68e1f52ed8347d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fe6f34056aa6bf3e2154bb5ef9e5a80b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;From London to Tokyo, this sound of traditional wooden drums has been invading the playlists of streaming music platforms for two years.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A house-derived electro music born in the townships of South Africa a decade ago, amapiano has gained a following around the world and brought African sounds to fans of commercial music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;"Amapiano is a whole cultural movement that is part of dance, it's a global language because you can have rappers on amapiano, you can have jazz musicians. It's not really melodic, there's no catchy element, it's more about the mood and the rhythm," is how Temi Adeniji, head of Warner Music Africa, describes amapiano.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In 2022, this musical style generated two billion streams on Spotify. There are over 240,000 amapiano playlists on the platform. Forty percent of the listening is outside South Africa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With our new amapiano collection, inspiration is guaranteed!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="afropopvibes_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="afropopvibes_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/VGefjX1VVC0"&gt;Afro Pop Vibes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ed0a504d76a1d4541917fe06bd06de46b681c501.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=69396883536f6adb74c2fbf26cc3e92e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Afro Pop Vibes' from Function Loops delivers all the sounds you need to get this genre running on your side!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drums, percussion, basslines, instrument loops, fx and also vocals hooks in dry and wet versions, to make your music outstanding! In addtion, you also get unique drum and synth shots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use in commercial projects, no strings attached.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cinematiccyberpunk_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="cinematiccyberpunk_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/wAwkpgxNee0"&gt;Cinematic Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/962e3f607f111471248d52e15a545fb925b52217.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cfd295e0e14b7de09dd62282ced7edf2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cinematic Cyberpunk' from Function Loops is a comprehensive collection of high-quality audio samples that is designed to transport you to a dystopian future filled with advanced technology, neon lights, and edgy synth sounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This sample pack is perfect for music producers, composers, and sound designers who are looking for the perfect sounds to add to their cyberpunk-inspired projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll find an extensive range of audio content, including gritty drum loops, haunting atmospheric textures, futuristic synth melodies, powerful basslines, and cutting-edge sound effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each sample has been carefully crafted to provide the authentic cyberpunk sound that is so popular in modern media.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Overall, the 'Cinematic Cyberpunk' sample pack is an essential tool for any producer or composer looking to create powerful, futuristic sounds that will take their listeners on a journey into the heart of a cyberpunk dystopia!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dreams_hiphopsessions_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="dreams_hiphopsessions_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/eGeoS6pG0wg"&gt;Dreams - Hip Hop Sessions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/da5010065cdbaaecadba7b70382dca75752b24fb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=99205bde64ba21bf6eb84b37d6d3183e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing 'Dreams - Hiphop Sessions' a captivating sample pack that seamlessly blends the vibrant elements of jazz and hip hop.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This meticulously crafted collection offers a original set of jazzy hip hop loops and shots, including drums, basses, pianos, guitars, and FX, to inspire your musical creations and elevate your production game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Immerse yourself in the infectious rhythms and grooves that define the essence of jazzy hip hop.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All the sounds are 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futureworldspsytrance_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futureworldspsytrance_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/LE-1h179IqU"&gt;Future Worlds Psytrance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1b6d865d8546f1870d65878dc1f7863a30046896.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8949bbdae8c0320d873d4f585012bfed"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Future Worlds - Psytrance Production Suite' is our latest collection that will take your studio by storm! Such a powerful production tool to improve your music, drastically.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A huge set of Loops, Stems, MIDI files, One Shots and Presets. 253 files in total!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We used the techniques of the titans to create this release, now you'll be able to use our sounds in your music, sell to labels and elevate your production career.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% royalty-free, collect all income to yourself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="astronautsci-fifx_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="astronautsci-fifx_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/hso6FB0ng9g"&gt;Astronaut Sci-Fi FX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8247e72484572b471083956c6c04523bcc4f4c6d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=76a78e12104665e746a841125a7235ff"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;For a long time in the works, it's finally here - new and never heard FX collection, that will take you on a trip to another dimension!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Several techniques used to create this unique sample pack, including foley in nature and in-house (capturing weird sounds), modulation, automation and a combination of hardware synths and software plugins, all connected into insane chains to generate these sounds - 100% original and never been used before!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Will improve your music drastically and add character to Psytrance, Techno, Dubstep, Drum&amp;amp;Bass, Electronica, Downtempo, Cinematic, Trip Hop, and other styles seeking some uniqueness.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to take the trip? You will experience something you never felt before.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="housevocalswithsandrah_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="housevocalswithsandrah_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/GRBsLzE4nrI"&gt;House Vocals with Sandrah&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c6f55f938b3e965fef7c0a65e61c0c18e56ccf7d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=72a1b64c7efa84ee0d2efcee7ccee1f5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are delighted to present to you a great new singer recently added to our already fine roster: Sandrah.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a true "diva in the making", Sandrah has a remarkable voice with an amazing range and colour, perfect for those classic House tracks which also fit beautifully into modern Deep or soulful House productions. Skillfully recorded, polished and produced, these lovely new acapellas will fit your next tracks right away.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A very useful collection of vocals, all coming as full multi-layered phrases, but with all the corresponding individual parts (main, doubling and harmony) as well. As usual, all the loops are available in their dry and effected variants, for maximum flexibility. The phrases can be used whole, or cut up into smaller bits and looped for that hypnotic club effect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vocalhookswithsandrah_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="vocalhookswithsandrah_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/QlFvfwFRZOY"&gt;Vocal Hooks with Sandrah&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5d1d6ddcffe8decbbc27cf93e0c2161ed44e9c41.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=931480c5195c7a2a1d7d4a01dbcf6e3c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Almost a month in the making, Sandrah is back with a brand new collection of gorgeous acapella loops, ready to be used in your latest productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new set of professionally recorded vocal loops is full of soul and character, reminiscent of famous soul divas we all so love and admire.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As always, you can use whole phrases or cut them up into smaller pieces for that hypnotic club effect. These vocals can be used for various genres, from house to funk, soul, garage, rnb, chill or acoustic productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coming as both dry and effected variants, these lovely new loops will keep you busy and surely inspire to make some stunning new tracks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find 120 loops, 30 vox chops, 50 one-shots, 200 files in total. Recorded at 24-bit WAV quality. 100% royalty-free content, which will add magic to your tracks. Give your track some life with this amazing and rare vocals collection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="astraltrancevocals_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="astraltrancevocals_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/2lXZrQA_ElM"&gt;Astral Trance Vocals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/897c83184e5667f46ca71d02b85201cd42492fba.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dc906a631086c72c93b5afd7e1069306"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Astral Trance Vocals offers the best solution for your next Trance and Psy productions. Recorded in absolute quality, these vocals are made to take your tracks to the big stages.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;552MB of vocal variations, fusion of cosmic, tribal, ethnic - it has it all.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vocals are coming in 2 versions:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Slightly reverbed - you can add your delays or other FX.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gated - we nailed the famous FX for you, great addition to any track.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add these vocals to your tracks and you will triple your music's quality, these vocals will give a completely different level to your productions, guaranteed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack was designed towards Trance and Psy, but the content can be useful in any other genre like Ambient, Drum &amp;amp; Bass, Tribal House, Techno and basically any other production, where hypnotic vocals are needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please note: all the instrumentals were taken from Progressive Psytrance &amp;amp; Festival Psytrance packs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vocalmomentswithsandrah_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="vocalmomentswithsandrah_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/2XJCUBVx5bE"&gt;Vocal Moments with Sandrah&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/57b6fa04a6dcaff043dd4d4579eb09db7b17ae0a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4203ce07e7237793588ded25de2da17f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Following the success of her two previous acapella packs, we bring Sandrah back to the studio for a fresh set of beautiful new vocal phrases, perfectly suited for your next productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These new acapellas come in various forms, from single vocal hooks, to full on harmonies. We also included a lovely selection of crispy vox shots, perfect for taking your grooves to next level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you need a classic-sounding collection of quality vocal phrases, but with a modern edge, this pack is a right choice for you. This pack will work great in House, Deep, Chill and even Techy genres or any other style where soulful vocals are needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="darkvocalsepisode2_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="darkvocalsepisode2_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/VrP2FbJ5gkU"&gt;Dark Vocals Episode 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f55ca6a80d2f7751ba52d8c3666c47ad665da8f4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=337ab4b62a255361ff96104fb1b81df5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;With the first volume of Dark Vocals selling hundreds of copies around the globe, we brought the devil back for another session this Halloween.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Who said we sold our souls?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dark Vocals: Episode 2 is way bigger than the first part, delivering 85 x Dry and 85 x Wet scary vocal loops. Unique content you won't find anywhere else, guaranteed. If you are into darker styles of music, this pack is the ultimate vocal solution.  Let's take a trip to the heart of hell!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="basshouseinvaders_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="basshouseinvaders_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/mFUFpAbrubk"&gt;Bass House Invaders!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3435d3971206541a3b735dacd543df1163ca4d5d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7485d1bb9661def73fd3de04a48c9fbb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bass House Invaders! from SHARP brings some crazy sounds on the table, so you can get inspired and drop some in your next tracks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5 x Key Labelled construction kits, packed with breaks, wobbles, basslines, leads, percussion, fx and vocal loops.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content 100% royalty-free, 24-bit WAV quality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;And remember - invaders must die :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hardtrapattack_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="hardtrapattack_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/vg1WQANaku8"&gt;Hard Trap Attack!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0b00e288ccb1ef406a929684e31e70e7c868e90b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=83b4c3a97d49491ffa59d3f6ecf08653"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hard Trap Attack! from SHARP (Function Loops Label Group) attacks your studio with the nastiest and hard sounds this genre can offer. Loaded with 7 x Key labelled Kits plus some kickass bonus Beats and 808s, this collection is guaranteed to blast some brains off.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each Kit serves all your needs with the latest Loops, Shots, MIDI files and Presets - the maximum flexibility at your production sessions. You are getting Drum Loops &amp;amp; Beats, Melodic Loops, Synths, hard Leads for insane Drops (where the crowd goes WOW), killer FX Loops and a bunch of other sh*t, absolutely guaranteed to take your productions to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% Royalty-Free, all Key &amp;amp; BPM labelled. Let's kill it!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="strictlyg-house_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="strictlyg-house_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/zTGp23byGNM"&gt;Strictly G-House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1ec7e5bbbab06e731931119e76a7cd99e840a38a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=67bdc814fff86bb1e24e1be0eecbb239"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A super fresh collection of G-House sounds coming from SHARP (Function Loops Label Group).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are getting an extra fat pack, loaded with 100 x Sylenth Presets and 5 x Key-labelled construction kits, each charged with Loops, Shots and MIDI files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sounds arrived from a ghost producer, which is coming from this scene, so he knows what he's doing. Instead of splitting the Kits and Soundbank into 2 different releases, we decided to spoil you and drop all sounds into this mega pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In detail, you are getting 20 x Bass, 20 x Plucks, 20 x Leads, 20 x Pads, 20 x FX presets for Sylenth VSTi. Each preset is an absolute helper while producing G-House, giving that serious vibe to your productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The 5 construction kits will help you start quicker than ever. They are packed with Drums, Basslines, Vocals, Leads, Effects and more, sounds produced using the Soundbank, so all the tools are synced perfectly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are getting crazy amount of stuff, no fillers. Over 340 files, pure G-House inspiration. All of that for 19.90$ only. This product can be useful for Deep Tech , Tech House and other genres.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also decided to add an exclusive Bonus to this pack, only for our website's customers! Let's get to business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psytrancestudioessentials_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="psytrancestudioessentials_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/Ow37F4VCt0s"&gt;Psytrance Studio Essentials&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d3529dafed73a4c74c05ce936e61c23539928017.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=371595a3569f753c21888d9f2243f344"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Psytrance Studio Essentials is a professional producer pack, loaded with all the essential elements needed to help you in your next tracks. Very long time in the making at Function Loops HQ, we finally reveal this amazing studio tool!  Perfectly crafted Bass Loops, Drum Loops, Music Loops, Atmospheres, FX Loops, various One-Shots, MIDI files and some extra presets for Massive, Sylenth, Serum and Spire VSTs. On top of all, you are also getting a bonus 2 minute multi-track kit from one of the demos, broken into full Stems, so you can see the arrangment. Loops also attached, if you wanna workout the kit in your own way. In total, there is 342 files in this monster production pack, loaded with latest sounds of Psytrance and Progressive Psy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grab this tool right now to improve your tracks in no time. All content is Key &amp;amp; BPM labelled, 100% Royalty-Free, produced by top ghost producer in the game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="melodicdeephouse_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="melodicdeephouse_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/tsqf-mN8Rf0"&gt;Melodic Deep House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ff91e96f479f2ddb9aea932f024d2178b144659b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ca1371cd28137a418e48574c6b79e4f8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Melodic Deep House from SHARP (Function Loops Label Group) offers a new tool set and a fresh doze of inspiration for Deep House producers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;6 Key labelled construction kits , loaded with Drums, Basslines, Melodies, Vocals, Pianos, Fx Loops and all the rest you hear in the demo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each kit is Key &amp;amp; BPM labelled, charged with al the essential tools: Loops, Shots, MIDI files and Presets for Sylenth &amp;amp; Massive VSTs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All content is 100% royalty-free.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack also, will be useful in other House sub-genres. Over 200 files to renew your creativity!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futuredeeptech_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="futuredeeptech_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/7G25NCnIoTI"&gt;Future Deep Tech&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a924c17f990ac9229dac7cf0e5c69c9b4fca0c2e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1e32b3663acd8482d7aba55e1796f17d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In "Future Deep Tech" you'll find all the needed elements to get you going, from signature subby basslines to moody riffs, lush pads, hypnotic grooves &amp;amp; vox hooks - it's all there.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack includes easy to use 7 x Key labelled construction kits , featuring various kinds of loops (bass, synths, vocals, SFX, drums, percussion), corresponding MIDI files and single shots. We also included a lovely sound bank for Spire to help you discover Deep Tech genre even further.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack will be handy also for Tech-House, Deep House, Techno etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psytrancebassvst_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="psytrancebassvst_functionloops"&gt;Psytrance Bass VST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5284c851d947d45e6445aa7df84cfb85db36b687.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0125948c1f44f342fa923483714b913a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed for rich, deep, and punchy basslines, this plugin brings rhythmic energy and warmth to any track. Packed with essential sound-shaping tools, it gives you full control over your low-end.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfectly tuned and ready to drop into your mix, this is the go-to bass solution for producers looking to craft professional, powerful basslines with ease.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="drumvaultvst_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="drumvaultvst_functionloops" href="https://youtu.be/AVCScTR5_lo"&gt;Drum Vault VST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/df01c41d963357adbba7f6b2b7fc86334c41d9d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2905f02096154fb1d5d690993d5c11ef"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get ready to level up your beats! With 133 expertly crafted drum kits across 3 expansions, DrumKit VST delivers 1,064 high-quality drum sounds covering Pop, RnB, House, Tech House, Hip Hop, Lofi &amp;amp; more. Whether you’re crafting chart-topping hits or vibey underground grooves, this versatile and easy-to-use plugin has you covered. Available in VST/VST3 (Windows) &amp;amp; VST/VST3/AU (Mac)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="royaltyfreemusicbonus_functionloops"&gt;&lt;a id="royaltyfreemusicbonus_functionloops"&gt;Royalty Free Music (BONUS)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="http